yle="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="">| 落槌總額為低估價107%，成交項目比率88%，數件時計精品刷新拍賣紀錄 |</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">手袋及配飾</span>現場拍賣成交總額港元4,900 萬 / 美元630 萬，見證佳士得十年來持續引領亞洲手袋拍賣市場</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="">| 落槌總額為低估價127%，成交項目比率97%&nbsp;|</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Artémis Domaines</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">單一藏家珍藏名酒</span>拍賣100%成交，成交總額港元2,600 萬 / 美元340 萬</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="">|&nbsp; 落槌總額為低估價180%；頂尖名莊珍罕佳釀吸引藏家熱切競逐 |</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="">|&nbsp; 進一步鞏固佳士得呈獻顯赫單一藏家珍藏的卓越能力 |&nbsp;</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" font-size:="" text-wrap:=""/><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">佳士得亞太區總裁龐智鋒</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">(Francis Belin)&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">表示：</span>&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「今年秋季，佳士得位於香港</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">The Henderson</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">的全新亞太區總部正式開幕，我們為此欣然呈獻一系列精心策劃的拍賣、博物館級預展及精彩活動，吸引全球藏家及藝術愛好者雲集一堂。香港</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">The Henderson</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">開幕系列拍賣彰顯佳士得在多個收藏類別的市場領軍地位，見證佳士得香港在亞洲中心為藏家呈獻全球藝術傑作與雅逸精品。今年下半年成交總額創下自</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">2021</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">年以來新高，亞洲藏家貢獻總額增幅顯著——中國內地及東南亞地區買家貢獻總額尤其卓著，新一代年輕買家亦展現強大購買力。系列開幕拍賣呈獻東西方名匠鉅作及顯赫單一藏家珍藏，二十及二十一世紀系列拍賣首先登場，推出西方及亞洲藍籌藝術家傑作，雅逸精品週拍賣亦取得璀璨佳績，亞洲藝術系列拍賣亦成績斐然，三大單一藏家珍藏均</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">100%</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">成交，再次彰顯佳士得在顯赫私人珍藏類別毋庸置疑的市場領軍地位。除拍賣外，</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">The Henderson</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">全新空間亦令我們得以透過多元展覽及活動與藏家深入互動，包括在亞洲首次舉行的日內瓦鐘錶大賞展覽、『迪拜鐘錶週』重要項目：鐘錶論壇，以及佳士得第九屆『</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Art+Tech</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">藝術科技峰會』等。我們十分期待於</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">2025</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">年在新總部推出全年不間斷的藝術及精品拍賣與精彩活動，在亞洲這一重要的國際平台繼續為全球藏家與愛好者帶來無與倫比的體驗。</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">」</em></p><p><br/></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('33','9','2024年全球預計成交總額美元57億','','2024年全球預計成交總額美元57億','','1','本年度最高成交價拍品由佳士得售出 私人洽購成交總額與去年同期相比增長41% 所有競投中81%來自網上平台香港亞洲2024 年12月18日佳士得行政總裁施俊安表示： 「我們很欣慰以積極樂觀的態度為2024年畫上句點，秋季系列拍賣勢頭更為強勁，Gooding & Co.的收購計劃也已完成。儘管藝術市場依然充滿挑戰，今年對佳士得而言是富有成效的一年。展望2025年及未來，我們充滿信心。…','1738996347','1738996495','<p>本年度最高成交價拍品由佳士得售出 私人洽購成交總額與去年同期相比增長41% 所有競投中81%來自網上平台<br/><br/><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac/hong-kong?lang=" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center; display: inline !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem;">香港</span></a><font face="ABC Arizona Sans, sans-serif"><br/></font><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: inline !important; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" line-height:="">亞洲</span></a><br/><a style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center; display: inline !important;"><span style="box-siz