/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>佳士得行政總裁施俊安表示：</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">&nbsp;</span></h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「我們很欣慰以積極樂觀的態度為</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">2024</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">年畫上句點，秋季系列拍賣勢頭更為強勁，</em></span></h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Gooding &amp; Co.</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">的收購計劃也已完成。儘管藝術市場依然充滿挑戰，</em></span></h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">今年對佳士得而言是富有成效的一年。展望</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">2025</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !importan