x; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">）</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">&nbsp;</em></span></p></li></ul><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><br/><br/></em></em></span></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="" text-align:="">2024年佳士得拍賣成績逐步穩固，私人洽購全年取得傲人成交。本年度拍賣總體成交比率86%，落槌總額為低估價112%，平均每件拍品吸引3.7位買家競投，與去年相比有所增長，見證我們的營運策略及業務重心滿足賣家和買家的多元需求。今年最高成交價藝術品為米卡·艾特根珍藏中的雷尼·馬格利特《光之帝國》，以美元1.212億的高價在佳士得售出；是今年全球唯一一件成交價超逾1億美元大關的拍品。今年最高成交價珠寶「The Eden Rose」亦由佳士得紐約在6月以美元1,340萬的高價售出。私人洽購總額增長41%，為全球成交總額的27%。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="" text-align:="">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="" text-align:="">2024全年期間，我們不斷自我投資以把握巨大增長機遇，佳士得藝術融資部（Christie’s Art Finance）持續擴展業務，為藝術傑作及雅逸精品提供貸款服務，佳士得創投基金（Christie’s Ventures）現已為12家充滿活力的高增長公司注資。佳士得全新亞太區總部於今年9月正式進駐香港The Henderson，迄今已吸引逾27,000位訪客蒞臨。9月我們亦宣布在沙特阿拉伯王國取得營業執照，這一重要地區此前已為佳士得業務貢獻良多。我們欣慰宣布完成收購Gooding &amp; Company，這間古董汽車拍賣行業的領軍拍賣行。Gooding Christie’s的2025年精彩日程將由2月於巴黎古董車展開啟，隨後將於3月6至7日舉行一年一度的愛美麗亞島拍賣。</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><br/><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><br/></em></em></span><br/></h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><br/></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; v