.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">嘉木留芳</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">─</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「木趣居」精選明式家具</span></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">所有拍品100%成交 | 落槌總額為低估價200%有餘</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">帕默家族典藏中國藝術</span></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">落槌總額為低估價105%</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">多個中國書畫單一藏家珍藏錄得斐然佳績，落槌總額為低估價</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">110%</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">有餘</span></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">包括王季遷家族舊藏；黃仲方珍藏中國書畫；梅潔樓珍藏；檳城駱清泉舊藏徐悲鴻傑作<br/><br/></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">現場拍賣精彩亮點:</span></p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">新一代年輕藏家踴躍參與競投</span></p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">買家總數增長16% | 首次參與佳士得拍賣的新買家總數增長20% | 千禧新世代買家總數增長29%</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">&nbsp;</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">中國內地及東南亞藏家貢獻卓著</span></p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">中國內地買家貢獻總額拔得頭籌 | 買家總數增長31%</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">東南亞買家貢獻成交總額增長23%</p><p></p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-size: 14.6667px;text-wrap: wrap"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">香港</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">&nbsp;</span>– 佳士得香港欣然宣布於2024年9月至11月在The Henderson亞太區新總部舉行的首屆亞洲藝術拍賣取得矚目佳績。 9月舉行的<a href="https://www.christies.com/zh/auction/the-au-bak-ling-collection-the-inaugural-sale-30463/" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)">「區百齡珍藏：首拍」</a>，以及11月首個亞洲藝術週期間舉行的<a href="https://www.christies.com/zh/events/asian-art-hong-kong/what-is-on?lid=3&sc_lang=zh" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)">六場亞洲藝術現場拍賣</a>共錄得成交總額<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">846,424,360 /&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">109,313,589</span>。系列拍賣呈獻中國瓷器及工藝精品和中國書畫佳作，由顯赫私人珍藏領銜，包括瓷器、古玉、古典家具、古代及近現代中國書畫等，再次彰顯佳士得為全球知名亞洲藝術私人珍藏拍賣的不二之選。拍賣吸引各方藏家於現場及線上平台積極參與競投，其中新一代年輕買家積極參與，新買家總數增長20%，七場現場拍賣的千禧新世代買家總數增長29%。佳士得香港嶄新亞太區總部憑藉博物館級展覽體驗和全年無間的靈活日程，與資深及新晉藏家和藝術愛好者深入互動。首個亞洲藝術週系列拍賣吸引大量中國內地和東南亞藏家熱切參與，中國內地買家貢獻總額拔得頭籌，東南亞買家貢獻成交總額更增長23%。本季拍賣取得的非凡佳績見證佳士得在亞洲藝術拍賣市場中毋庸置疑的領軍地位，亦彰顯藝術市場依然充滿澎湃活力和旺盛需求。</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap">佳士得香港|亞洲藝術現場拍賣佳績一覽</h3><hr style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-size: 14.6667px;text-wrap: wrap"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">中國書畫| 11月27-28日</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">秋季現場拍賣成交總額</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">:&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">2.72</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">/</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">3,500</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">萬</span></p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>持續兩日的拍賣吸引各方藏家熱切競投，落槌總額為低估價 114% ， 40% 拍品以逾高估價成交</p></li><li><p>新一代年輕買家湧入拍場: 近20% 買家為首次參與佳士得拍賣，其中32%为千禧世代</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">佳士得香港中國書畫部於11月27至28日舉行兩場現場拍賣，共錄得成交總額港元271,929,160 /美元35,101,160。中國古代書畫拍賣以吳歴《陶圃松菊圖》領銜，成交價高達港元43,935,000 /美元5,671,218，超逾低估價1.7倍有餘。中國近現代及當代書畫拍賣最高成交價拍品則為來自重要及顯赫歐洲貴族收藏的吳冠中傑作《桂林日出》, 成交價達港元12,475,000 /美元1,610,298，超逾低估價2.7倍有餘。兩場拍賣萃選一系列來源有緒的顯赫單一藏家珍藏，包括王季遷家族舊藏、黃仲方珍藏中國書畫、梅潔樓珍藏及檳城駱清泉舊藏徐悲鴻傑作，落槌總額各為低估價110%有餘。&nbsp;</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-size: 14.6667px;text-wrap: wrap"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">中國瓷器及工藝精品| 9月26日及11月29日</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">秋季現場拍賣成交總額：港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">5.745</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">7,420</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">萬</span></p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>五場現場拍賣落槌總額為低估價147%，51%拍品成交價超逾高估價</p></li><li><p>傲領秋季拍賣市場：成交總額創下自2017年秋季以來新高，見證佳士得在亞洲藝術拍賣市場毋庸置疑的領軍地位，同時彰顯藝術市場充滿澎湃活力和旺盛需求</p></li><li><p>大量新買家參與競投，新買家總數增長92%，千禧新世代買家總數增長41%</p></li><li><p>網上平台競投踴躍，透過數碼平台投得拍品的買家總數增長36%</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">單一藏家珍藏專場拍賣</span></p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><a href="https://press.christies.com/inaugural-evening-sales-at-the-henderson-sale-total-hk112b-us145m-tc?lang=zho" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)">區百齡珍藏：首拍</a></p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">100%成交 | 落槌總額為低估價160%</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><a href="https://press.christies.com/cosmic-essence-archaic-jades-from-the-lantien-shanfang-collection-sale-total-hk215m-us28m-tc?lang=zho" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)">太一精魄─藍田山房舊藏古玉</a></p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">100%成交 | 落槌總額近低估價600%</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><a href="https://press.christies.com/eternal-ming-treasures-from-the-mqj-collection-dedicated-live-auction-sale-total-hk564m-us73m-tc?lang=zho" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)">嘉木留芳─「木趣居」精選明式家具</a></p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">100%成交 | 落槌總額為低估價200%有餘</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>帕默家族典藏中國藝術</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">成交項目比率92% | 落槌總額為低估價105%</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 390.435px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">佳士得香港中國瓷器及藝術品部於9月26日及11月29日舉行五場現場拍賣，共錄得成交總額港元574,495,200 / 美元74,194,618，鞏固佳士得作為中國瓷器及工藝精品各大類別拍賣的龍頭地位。本季呈獻的三場單一藏家珍藏專場拍賣均取得100%成交的璀璨佳績，包括區百齡珍藏、太一精魄─藍田山房舊藏古玉、嘉木留芳─「木趣居」精選明式家具，彰顯佳士得在中國瓷器、古玉及中國古典家具市場中無可置疑的領軍地位。此外，帕默家族典藏中國藝術落槌總額為低估價105%。重要中國瓷器及工藝精品拍賣的領銜拍品為明宣德青花吹簫引鳳圖盌，以港元30,625,000 / 美元3,955,142的高價成為香港首屆亞洲藝術週拍賣的最高成交價拍品。</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-size: 14.6667px;text-wrap: wrap"/><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap">各場拍賣最高成交價拍品</h3><p><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/4101738996924.png" width="1482" height="814"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/93631738996928.png" width="1481" height="787"/><img src="https://christies.epresspack.me/storage/clients/641/image_-_2024-12-03T104433.774_1733193886.png" width="1481" height="802"/><a class="details__date" style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); display: inline !important; text-decoration: underline;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"></span></a><br/></p><p></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('35','9','2024年秋季雅逸精品系列拍賣 迄今成交總額: 港元8.04億 / 美元1.04億 勢將引領2024年拍賣市場 ','','2024年秋季雅逸精品系列拍賣 迄今成交總額: 港元8.04億 / 美元1.04億 勢將引領2024','','1','精心策劃的拍賣取得強勁成交 成交項目比率92% | 落槌總額為低估價106%&nbsp;香港亞洲2024 年11月2日瑰麗珠寶、精緻名錶、手袋及名酒拍賣錄得璀璨佳績瑰麗珠寶及翡翠首飾拍賣本季成交總額港元4.66億（美元6,000萬）落槌總額為低估價106%，成交項目比率92%，見證亞洲藏家收藏激情精緻名錶拍賣成交總額港元2.11億（美元2,700萬）落槌總額為低估價107%，成交項目比率88%，數&hellip;','1738997727','1738997727','<p><span style="font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 18.6667px; text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap;">精心策劃的拍賣取得強勁成交 成交項目比率92% | 落槌總額為低估價106%&nbsp;</span></p><p><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac/hong-kong?lang=" target="_self"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.6875rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.8125rem;">香港</span><span style="font-family:ABC Arizona Serif, serif"><span style="font-size: 18.6667px;"><br/></span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.6875rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.8125rem;">亞洲</span><span style="font-family:ABC Arizona Serif, serif"><span style="font-size: 18.6667px;"><br/></span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.6875rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.8125rem;">2024 年11月2日</span></a><br/><br/></p><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">瑰麗珠寶、精緻名錶、手袋及名酒拍賣錄得璀璨佳績</span></h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">瑰麗珠寶及翡翠首飾</span>拍賣本季成交總額港元4.66億（美元6,000萬）</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">落槌總額為低估價106%，成交項目比率92%，見證亞洲藏家收藏激情</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">精緻名錶</span>拍賣成交總額港元2.11億（美元2,700萬）</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">落槌總額為低估價107%，成交項目比率88%，數件時計精品刷新拍賣紀錄</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">手袋及配飾</span>拍賣年度成交總額逾港元1.4億（美元1,800萬）</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">秋季拍賣成交總額港元4,900萬（美元630萬），落槌總額為低估價127%，成交項目比率97%</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Artémis Domaines</span>單一藏家珍藏名酒拍賣<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">100%</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">成交，</span>成交總額港元2,600萬（美元340萬）</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">落槌總額為低估價180%，珍罕佳釀吸引藏家熱切競逐</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">吸引新一代年輕藏家積極參與競投</span></h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">首次參與佳士得拍賣新買家總數增長32%（現場與網上拍賣總計新買家增長74%）</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">51%新買家為千禧新世代</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">網上平台競投踴躍</span></h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span class="TextRun SCXW233997538 BCX8" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">網上平台為最重要購買渠道</span><span class="TextRun SCXW233997538 BCX8" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">;&nbsp;</span><span class="TextRun SCXW233997538 BCX8" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">52%</span><span class="TextRun SCXW233997538 BCX8" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">買家透過網上競投平台投得拍品</span><span class="EOP SCXW233997538 BCX8" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">&nbsp;</span></h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">拍賣吸引來自全球六大洲59個國家的買家積極參與&nbsp;&nbsp;</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">亞太區買家貢獻卓著</span></h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">亞太區購買總額與2023年秋季相比顯著增長16%</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">東南亞買家購買總額增長高達138%，日本買家購買總額增長182%，台灣買家購買總額增長124%</h5><p><br/></p><p><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/52921738997647.png" width="612" height="132" style="float: left; width: 612px; height: 132px;" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">香港 – 佳士得香港欣然宣布在The Henderson舉行的首個雅逸精品拍賣週取得圓滿成功，2024年秋季拍賣迄今為止共錄得<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">成交總額港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">8.36</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">1.08</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">億</span>。<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">總體成交項目比率</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">92%</span>，<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">落槌總額為低估價</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">106%</span>。本季取得的斐然佳績見證佳士得專家團隊精心策劃的拍賣滿足廣大雅逸精品藏家的多元喜好，同時鞏固佳士得即將引領2024年<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">亞洲精品拍賣市場</span>的強勁勢頭。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">我們將亞太區總部遷至The Henderson的創舉成功令佳士得以更有活力的方式與藏家互動。本季拍賣的買家來源見證我們的影響力日益深入，新買家總數與2023年秋季相比增長32%（現場與網上拍賣總計新買家增長74%）。本季約三分之一買家為首次參與佳士得拍賣，逾半數買家為千禧新世代，見證我們成功吸引新一代年輕買家參與拍賣。可圈可點的是，亞太區買家貢獻總額與2023年秋季相比增長16%，東南亞買家貢獻增長達138%，日本和台灣買家貢獻分別增長182%和124%，彰顯區內藏家熾熱需求和購藏實力。今季取得的斐然佳績鞏固佳士得對雅逸精品市場的強大信心。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">數碼平台是本季藏家參與競投的重要方式，52%買家透過網上平台投得藏品，拍賣現場直播吸引逾670萬觀眾登入收看。拍賣吸引來自全球六大洲59個國家的買家積極參與。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">佳士得The Henderson亞太區新總部的博物館級藝廊現已成為藝術與精品藏家的首選目的地。三場精彩活動亦於十月在佳士得拉開帷幕，包括日內瓦鐘錶大賞（GPHG）、第十屆鐘錶論壇（Horology Forum）及第九屆Art+Tech藝術科技峰會，均吸引大量訪客蒞臨參加並獲得熱烈反響，足以見證佳士得The Henderson嶄新空間為世界頂級藝術與精品的殿堂，匯聚全球藏家於此溝通對話。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">不久後，我們將於11月7日在上海舉辦二十及二十一世紀晚間拍賣，並於11月9日在香港舉辦二十及二十一世紀日間拍賣，隨後將於11月末（27至29日）隆重舉辦新總部首屆亞洲藝術拍賣週。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">佳士得香港</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">|&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">雅逸精品系列拍賣佳績一覽</span></p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">珍罕名釀及烈酒</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;| 10</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">4</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">日、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">26</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">日及</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">30</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">日</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;"></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">亞洲年度成交總額：港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">1.8</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">2,300</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">萬</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">秋季（現場及網上）拍賣迄今成交總額：港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">7,700</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">萬</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">1,000</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">萬<br/><br/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/29621738997647.png" width="748" height="321"/><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 630.992px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">佳士得香港共呈獻三場珍罕名釀及烈酒現場拍賣及兩場網上拍賣，迄今成交總額<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">77,687,662&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">10,045,217</span>萬。本季的精彩策劃取得<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">92%</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">成交項目比率</span>。現場拍賣新買家總數與2023年秋季相比增長150%， 其中，50%新買家為千禧新世代，見證名酒收藏的近期趨勢變化。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 630.992px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">佳士得於春季呈獻「不朽傳奇窖藏名釀第一部份」並取得斐然佳績，本季繼續榮幸呈獻「<a href="https://www.christies.com/en/auction/the-epic-cellar-part-ii-30572/?&lid=3&sc_lang=zh" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">不朽傳奇窖藏名釀第二部份</span></a>」，總體成交比率92%，落槌總額為低估價88%。除此之外，<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">「</span><a href="https://www.christies.com/en/auction/a-life-well-lived-the-remarkable-cellar-of-melina-and-dr-n-k-yong-30573/?&lid=3&sc_lang=zh" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">卓越人生：</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">N.K. Yong</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">醫生伉儷窖藏珍釀</span></a>」現場及網上拍賣成交項目比率90%，見證藏家四十餘年來的收藏熱忱和慷慨友誼。另有「<a href="https://www.christies.com/en/auction/direct-from-the-cellars-art-mis-domaines-30570/?&lid=3&sc_lang=zh" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">酒窖直遞：</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">Art</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">é</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-weight: 700 !important">mis Domaines</span></a>」拍賣，標誌著佳士得首度為Artémis Domaines舉行專拍，精選一系列來自全球最受渴求的頂尖名莊、跨越兩世紀的珍罕名釀，更取得100%成交的佳績，落槌總額為低估價180%。這一精心策劃的專拍見證酒莊始終堅守對卓越品質的追求，以世上珍罕難尋的佳釀吸引藏家熱烈競投。</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-size: 14.6667px;text-wrap: wrap"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 630.992px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">精緻名錶</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">&nbsp;| 10</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">27</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: ba