rder: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">210,836,060&nbsp;</span>/&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">27,248,768</span>，<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">成交項目比率</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">88%</span>，<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">落槌總額為拍前低估價</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">107%</span>，可見佳士得精選富有歷史意義的頂級時計對市場具有强大吸引力。拍賣共吸引來自全球六大洲53個國家買家的激烈競投，其中52%的藏家透過網絡平台投得藏品，彰顯香港作為國際拍賣平台的重要地位。拍賣吸引大量新一代年輕藏家積極參與競投，現場拍賣新買家總數與2023年秋季相比增長54%（現場及網上拍賣總計新買家增長308%）。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 630.992px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important">極為珍稀的<span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">百達翡麗型號</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">1518</span>矚目領銜拍賣，以港元19,130,000 / 美元2,472,390的高價強勁成交，見證全球藏家與鐘錶愛好者對頂級時計青睞有加。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transit