.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">&nbsp;/</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">1.28</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">億</span></p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>勢將取得2024年市場領軍地位</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;margin-top: 25px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14.6667px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;width: 630.992px;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.35em !important"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">秋季現場拍賣成交總額</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">:&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">港元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">4.67</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">6,000</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;font-weight: 700 !important">萬</span></p><p><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/40721738997659.png" width="594" height="321" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 594px; height: 321px;"/></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('37','9','首個亞洲藝術週中國瓷器及工藝精品現場拍賣呈獻洋洋大觀、來源有緒的全球顯赫私人珍藏','','亞洲藝術','','1','亞洲藝術香港亞洲2024 年10月10日香港—佳士得欣然宣布於香港The Henderson的全新亞太區總部舉行首個亞洲藝術週，並於2024年11月29日呈獻四場中國瓷器及工藝精品現場拍賣，包括稍早公布的「嘉木留芳─『木趣居』精選明式家具」專場現場拍賣。精彩紛呈的拍賣萃選各地來源非凡的重要罕見珍藏，四場拍賣的總低估價逾港元3.5億。帕默家族典藏中國藝術佳士得於2023年5月推出歐洲舉足輕重的帕默家&hellip;','1739023022','1739023022','<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/press-releases/asian-art?lang=zho" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 0.875rem;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Sans&#39;, sans-serif;line-height: 1.0625rem;text-align: center;text-wrap: wrap"><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/press-releases/asian-art?lang=zho" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.0625rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); text-decoration: underline;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.0625rem; text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">亞洲藝術</span></a><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac/hong-kong?lang=" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="20" height="20" viewbox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M16.5229 6.79484C16.5229 7.6411 16.1325 8.84479 15.4981 10.2187C14.8707 11.5774 14.0307 13.0487 13.1856 14.4113C12.3413 15.7725 11.4964 17.0179