/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/4801739023731.jpg" width="594" height="321"/></p><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">為西方藍籌藝術家及亞洲藝壇巨匠傑作提供國際重要平台</span></h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">文森特·梵高(1853-1890)，《停泊的船隻》：港元2.51億 /美元3,240萬</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">克勞德·莫奈 (1840-1926) ，《睡蓮》：港元2.33億 / 美元3,010萬</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">趙無極 (1920-2013) ， 《05.06.80 - 三聯作》：港元9,500萬 /美元1,230萬</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">金煥基 (1913-1974) ，《9-XII-71 #216》：港元5,600萬 / 美元720萬</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">&nbsp;</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">亞洲拍賣史上成交價最高的六大西方藝術鉅作中</span></h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">四件於佳士得成交</span></h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">系列拍賣共刷新</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">8</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">位藝術家世界拍賣紀錄</span></h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">亞洲藝術家矚目領銜</span></h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">&nbsp;</span></h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">精心策劃的拍賣吸引新一代年輕藏家&nbsp;</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">拍賣現場直播共吸引620萬人次觀看</h4><h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" text-align:="">The Henderson拍賣預展吸引12,840位訪客蒞臨</h4><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Hong Kong</span>&nbsp;– 2024年9月26至27日, 佳士得香港於The Henderson亞太區新總部呈獻二十及二十一世紀系列三場開幕拍賣，共錄得成交總額港元1,256,203,200 / 美元162,203,684，成交項目比率92%，見證區內藏家熱烈參與競投。佳士得精心策劃拍賣，推出來自東西方藍籌藝術家的精彩力作，繼續滿足亞洲藏家的多元購藏需求。系列拍賣領銜拍品為文森特·梵高鉅作《停泊的船隻》，成交價高達港元250,625,000/</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em="">美元32,359,071，趙無極《05.06.80 - 三聯作》亦以港元95,375,000 / 美元12,314,200的高價成交。拍賣預展吸引12,840位訪客蒞臨欣賞，更有620萬人次登入網絡平台觀看拍賣現場直播。系列拍賣持續吸引新一代年輕藏家參與競投。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" text-wrap:="" line-height:="" 1.35em=""><a href="https://press.christies.com/christies-2024-inaugural-evening-sales-at-the-henderson" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-transform: inherit !important;">按此</a>瀏覽區百齡珍藏及二十及二十一世紀晚間拍賣新聞稿。</p><p><br/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/12091739023731.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/79891739023731.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/19181739023731.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/56771739023731.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/22491739023732.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/36951739023732.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/6681739023732.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/62541739023733.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/49711739023733.jpg" width="594" height="321"/><br/></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('39','9','佳士得香港THE HENDERSON 全新亞太區總部正式開幕','','世界級藝術傑作及雅逸精品樞紐 全年提供精彩體驗','','1','世界級藝術傑作及雅逸精品樞紐 全年提供精彩體驗香港亞洲2024 年9月20日香港 — 9月20日，佳士得位於The Henderson的全新亞太區總部正式開幕。這座全新地標式建築坐落於香港中環，由國際知名的扎哈·哈迪德建築事務所(Zaha Hadid Architects)設計。而佳士得亞洲的全新頂級旗艦空間則設於六至九樓，佔地50,000平方英尺，設有世界一流的拍賣廳、藝廊、客戶專屬空…','1739024032','1739024070','<p><span style="font-family: " abc="" arizona="" font-size:="" text-align:="" text-wrap:="">世界級藝術傑作及雅逸精品樞紐 全年提供精彩體驗<a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac/hong-kong?lang=" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="20" height="20" viewbox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M16.5229 6.79484C16.5229 7.6411 16.1325 8.84479 15.4981 10.2187C14.8707 11.5774 14.0307 13.0487 13.1856 14.4113C12.3413 15.7725 11.4964 17.0179 10.8622 17.9234C10.5628 18.3508 10.3107 18.7021 10.1281 18.9536C9.9455 18.7021 9.69338 18.3508 9.39403 17.9234C8.75982 17.0179 7.91488 15.7725 7.07059 14.4113C6.22547 13.0487 5.38548 11.5774 4.7581 10.2187C4.12364 8.84479 3.73325 7.6411 3.73325 6.79484C3.73325 5.09882 4.40699 3.47227 5.60626 2.27301C6.80552 1.07374 8.43208 0.4 10.1281 0.4C11.8241 0.4 13.4507 1.07374 14.6499 2.27301C15.8492 3.47227 16.5229 5.09882 16.5229 6.79484Z" stroke="black" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M11.9929 6.79522C11.9929 7.8252 11.158 8.66017 10.128 8.66017C9.098 8.66017 8.26304 7.8252 8.26304 6.79522C8.26304 5.76524 9.098 4.93027 10.128 4.93027C11.158 4.93027 11.9929 5.76524 11.9929 6.79522Z" stroke="black" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><span style="text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap; box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: " abc="" arizona="" line-height:="" color:="">香港</span></a><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="26" height="26" viewbox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.2211 16.57L6.22116 16.57L6.21892 16.5647C5.88157 15.7673 5.81287 14.9508 6.01225 14.1073C6.21267 13.2594 6.60316 12.53 7.18437 11.9142C8.40538 10.921 9.12263 9.87932 9.26397 8.78395L9.26522 8.77423L9.26571 8.76444C9.30174 8.04389 9.04818 7.29968 8.54044 6.53808C8.03995 5.78734 7.48525 5.17216 6.87459 4.69719L6.7211 4.57782L6.56761 4.69719C3.86973 6.79555 2.51602 9.57033 2.51602 13C2.51602 14.732 2.90778 16.3583 3.69136 17.8755C4.47397 19.3907 5.53383 20.6186 6.8707 21.5544L7.26407 21.8298V21.3496C7.26407 19.9099 6.91273 18.3156 6.2211 16.57ZM8.86441 22.5511L8.85078 22.7284L9.01378 22.7995C10.3159 23.3671 11.7009 23.6504 13.1664 23.6504C16.0976 23.6504 18.6107 22.6066 20.6918 20.5254C22.773 18.4443 23.8168 15.9312 23.8168 13C23.8168 11.964 23.6497 10.8665 23.3189 9.70866L23.2742 9.5523L23.1132 9.52976L15.8719 8.51598L13.0805 5.72461L13.6362 5.16896L15.7358 3.06935L16.0443 2.76082L15.6221 2.65067C14.851 2.44951 14.0321 2.34961 13.1664 2.34961C11.3445 2.34961 9.77178 2.69748 8.45804 3.40488L8.15662 3.56719L8.40298 3.8049C10.2293 5.56716 11.0017 7.26942 10.8183 8.91966L10.8182 8.91964L10.8175 8.92809C10.7271 10.1041 9.92056 11.4959 8.30996 13.1084C7.88842 13.4623 7.61032 13.8872 7.49123 14.3819C7.37197 14.8773 7.41707 15.4218 7.60629 16.0066L7.61009 16.0184L7.61503 16.0297C8.61085 18.3105 9.0235 20.4831 8.86441 22.5511ZM16.6555 7.02815L16.7137 7.0839L16.7935 7.09519L21.9693 7.82761L22.4796 7.89982L22.2204 7.45435C21.15