3 21.8275 4.33889C24.2221 6.73344 25.4164 9.61583 25.4164 13C25.4164 16.3842 24.2221 19.2666 21.8275 21.6611C19.433 24.0557 16.5506 25.25 13.1664 25.25C9.78224 25.25 6.89985 24.0557 4.5053 21.6611C2.11074 19.2666 0.916412 16.3842 0.916412 13C0.916412 9.61583 2.11074 6.73344 4.5053 4.33889Z" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"></path></svg><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">全球</span></a><a style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="21" height="21" viewbox="0 0 21 21" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="0.5" y="1.80005" width="20" height="18.2" stroke="#8C1A11"></rect><path d="M0.675049 7.8125H20.3375" stroke="#8C1A11"></path><path d="M14.625 0L14.625 5" stroke="#8C1A11"></path><path d="M6.375 0L6.375 5" stroke="#8C1A11"></path><rect x="3.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="3.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="3.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="7.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="7.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="7.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="11.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="11.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="11.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="15.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="15.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="15.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect></svg><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">2024 年9月12日</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 0.5625rem;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: row;justify-content: center;align-items: center;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Sans&#39;, sans-serif;line-height: 0.6875rem"><br/><br/><br/></span></a></p><p><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/26991739024232.png" width="594" height="321"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">紐約</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span>– 佳士得欣然宣布已與汽車收藏市場中的國際頂尖拍賣行Gooding &amp; Company達成收購協議。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">Gooding &amp; Company是由David Gooding和Dawn Ahrens夫妻二人於2003年創立的汽車拍賣行，多年來享譽全球，可謂古董汽車拍賣行業的領軍。公司一貫秉持卓越誠信品格和透明度，致力提供一流汽車拍賣服務，並因此聞名於世。Gooding &amp; Company一直為藏家甄選來自顯赫典藏、家族祖傳珍藏及重新面世的迷人古董車款，深受業界敬仰。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">本次收購乃佳士得歷史上的重要里程碑，奠定我們在快速擴張的古董車和汽車收藏市場中的重要地位，同時更進一步鞏固其於雅逸精品市場中的領導地位。佳士得和Gooding &amp; Company在精品銷售領域之專業知識、誠信品格和卓越客戶服務方面擁有共同的價值觀，兩者雙璧合一，無疑是最理想的組合。這項併購方案將為Gooding &amp; Company提供更強大全面的全球平台，以支援其未來的成長和品牌發展。Gooding &amp; Company仍將繼續致力為其忠實客戶提供最優質的服務，透過久負盛名的展覽、拍賣等更多精彩活動回饋藏家。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">收購協議完成後，Gooding &amp; Company將更名為Gooding Christie’s。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">佳士得行政總裁施俊安（</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Guillaume Cerutti</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">）</span>表示：<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「佳士得長期以來一直很欣賞</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Gooding &amp; Company</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">品牌及其營運方式。</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">David Gooding</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">和團隊在過去二十年間所創造的輝煌成就令全球藏家都深感敬佩，因此他們選擇加入佳士得令我們感到莫大的榮幸。我們相信雙方資源結合將帶來諸多機會，推動全球業務顯著增長。」</em></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Gooding &amp; Company</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">共同創辦人暨總裁</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">David Gooding</span>指出：<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「二十一年前，我們以誠信、品質和熱忱為核心創立了</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Gooding &amp; Company</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">，正式踏入汽車收藏市場。我們在這一行業中的高速增長令我深感自豪，我堅信佳士得的收購將推動我們持續發展，持續引領全球汽車收藏市場。我十分期待與</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Guillaume</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">及佳士得團隊通力合作，帶領</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Gooding &amp; Company</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">邁入全新時代。」</em></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Artémis&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">集團主席</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Fran</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">ç</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">ois-Henri Pinault</span>表示：<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「我很高興見證佳士得收購</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Gooding &amp; Company</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">。</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">David Gooding</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">及其團隊的雄心壯志與佳士得一拍即合，同時也與</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Pinault</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">家族長期在藝術和文化、精品和生活方式等領域投資的其他事業一脈相承。我們很欣慰能夠支持</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Gooding &amp; Company</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">的發展並探索新的合作機會。」</em></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">收購預計於2024年底前完成。佳士得特聘Rothschild &amp; Co擔任財務顧問，並由Alston &amp; Bird擔任法律顧問。Gooding &amp; Company則由Allen &amp; Company擔任財務顧問，由盛信律師事務所擔任法律顧問。</p><p><br/></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('41','9','佳士得宣布將於香港舉行第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」','','九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」','','1','佳士得宣布將於香港舉行第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」香港亞洲2024 年9月12日門票：佳士得第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」香港門票現可於https://www.christies.com/art-tech-hk-ticketing購買&nbsp;萬勿錯過本次寶貴機會，在匯聚創意和尖端科技的峰會中體驗創意先鋒的超前理念。&nbsp;地點：香港 | 10月29日 | 佳士得全新亞太區&hellip;','1739024346','1739024346','<h1 class="single-template__main-content--title heading" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 32px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;text-align: center;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-weight: 300;line-height: 1.35em;width: 390.435px;text-wrap: wrap;align-self: flex-start !important">佳士得宣布將於香港舉行第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」</h1><p><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac/hong-kong?lang=" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="20" height="20" viewbox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M16.5229 6.79484C16.5229 7.6411 16.1325 8.84479 15.4981 10.2187C14.8707 11.5774 14.0307 13.0487 13.1856 14.4113C12.3413 15.7725 11.4964 17.0179 10.8622 17.9234C10.5628 18.3508 10.3107 18.7021 10.1281 18.9536C9.9455 18.7021 9.69338 18.3508 9.39403 17.9234C8.75982 17.0179 7.91488 15.7725 7.07059 14.4113C6.22547 13.0487 5.38548 11.5774 4.7581 10.2187C4.12364 8.84479 3.73325 7.6411 3.73325 6.79484C3.73325 5.09882 4.40699 3.47227 5.60626 2.27301C6.80552 1.07374 8.43208 0.4 10.1281 0.4C11.8241 0.4 13.4507 1.07374 14.6499 2.27301C15.8492 3.47227 16.5229 5.09882 16.5229 6.79484Z" stroke="black" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M11.9929 6.79522C11.9929 7.8252 11.158 8.66017 10.128 8.66017C9.098 8.66017 8.26304 7.8252 8.26304 6.79522C8.26304 5.76524 9.098 4.93027 10.128 4.93027C11.158 4.93027 11.9929 5