 height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect></svg><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">2024 年9月12日</span></a></p><p><br/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/64271739024335.png" width="594" height="321"/></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">門票：</span></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">佳士得第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」香港門票</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">現可於<a href="https://www.christies.com/art-tech-hk-ticketing" style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-transform: inherit !important;">https://www.christies.com/art-tech-hk-ticketing</a>購買</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">萬勿錯過本次寶貴機會，在匯聚創意和尖端科技的峰會中體驗創意先鋒的超前理念。</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">地點：</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">香港 | 10月29日 | 佳士得全新亞太區總部</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">— 中環美利道2號The Henderson</h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">香港</span>——佳士得欣然宣布將於<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">10</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">29</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">日</span>盛大舉行第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」。第八屆峰會於2024年7月在紐約圓滿落幕，深入探討時尚界的可持續發展和人工智能，以至藝術市場現況等議題。如今峰會回歸充滿活力的香港，進一步鞏固佳士得引領全球藝術傑作、雅逸精品和尖端科技的領先地位。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">與香港金融科技周（2024年10月28日至11月1日）同期舉行的峰會為期一天，將會探討<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">人工智能</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">(AI)</span>、<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">數碼藝術</span>和<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">金融科技</span>等嶄新科技的劃時代影響，並會舉行多場講座、會談和座談會，涵蓋「人工智能時代的投資策略」、「今日市場中的數碼藝術收藏」及「數碼金融時代的量化信譽」等主題。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">本屆峰會中，我們榮幸邀請到各界嘉賓，包括元宇宙先鋒The Sandbox聯合創辦人及營運總監Sébastien Borget先生，及摩根大通私人銀行亞洲行政總裁彭思佳（Harshika Patel）女士作為主要嘉賓發言。他們的獨特見解將為藝術界中新興技術的討論帶來更多豐富內容。除此之外，峰會亦邀請各界不同代表參加，呈現藝術與科技界中的不同視角與專業意見。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">知名數碼藝術家Beeple（本名Mike Winkelmann）亦將透過Zoom以遠程方式參與峰會。2021年，Beeple的作品在佳士得以美元6,900萬的高價拍出，標誌著純數碼藝術作品首次公開登上拍場，Beeple亦憑藉此作一躍成為當時全球身價最高昂的數碼藝術藝術家。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">第九屆「Art+Tech藝術科技峰會」將於佳士得全新亞太區總部The Henderson舉行，為與會者提供寶貴機會，與引領藝術界未來發展的創新先鋒、藝術家和創意先驅互動交流。佳士得希望透過這個生機勃勃的平台與各界分享知識並促成合作，藉此鼓勵全球藝術和科技社群繼續開拓全新的創意表達和收藏方式。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">佳士得亞太區總裁龐智鋒</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">(Francis Belin)</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span>表示：<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「香港作為國際藝術及金融樞紐，是探索創意與科技的最佳地點。我們很高興能在這座充滿活力的城市舉行『</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Art+Tech</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">藝術科技峰會』，同時透過全年的精彩活動為藏家和藝術界帶來啟發靈感。」</em></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">佳士得風險投資部全球主管</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">Devang Thakkar</span>指：<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「第九屆『</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Art+Tech</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">藝術科技峰會』雲集藝術、金融和科技界的傑出人才，將會成為孕育創新意念和推動合作的理想平台，為相關行業開創光明未來。」</em></p><p><br/></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('42','9','2024年上半年全球成交總額達美元21億','','2024年上半年全球成交總額達美元21億','','1','2024年上半年全球成交總額達美元21億香港全球2024 年7月17日佳士得行政總裁施俊安表示：&nbsp;「雖然佳士得的成交總額略為下降，但上半年的拍賣業務仍然穩定。面對充滿考驗的宏觀經濟環境，我們維持並提高衡量業績表現的各項關鍵指標。」&nbsp;美元21億 拍賣成交總額&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&hellip;','1739024441','1739024441','<h1 class="single-template__main-content--title heading" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 32px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;text-align: center;font-family: &#39;ABC Arizona Serif&#39;, serif;font-weight: 300;line-height: 1.35em;width: 390.435px;text-wrap: wrap;align-self: flex-start !important"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px">2024</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px">年上半年全球成交總額達美元21</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px">億</strong></h1><p><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/apac/hong-kong?lang=" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="20" height="20" viewbox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M16.5229 6.79484C16.5229 7.6411 16.1325 8.84479 15.4981 10.2187C14.8707 11.5774 14.0307 13.0487 13.1856 14.4113C12.3413 15.7725 11.4964 17.0179 10.8622 17.9234C10.5628 18.3508 10.3107 18.7021 10.1281 18.9536C9.9455 18.7021 9.69338 18.3508 9.39403 17.9234C8.75982 17.0179 7.91488 15.7725 7.07059 14.4113C6.22547 13.0487 5.38548 11.5774 4.7581 10.2187C4.12364 8.84479 3.73325 7.6411 3.73325 6.79484C3.73325 5.09882 4.40699 3.47227 5.60626 2.27301C6.80552 1.07374 8.43208 0.4 10.1281 0.4C11.8241 0.4 13.4507 1.07374 14.6499 2.27301C15.8492 3.47227 16.5229 5.09882 16.5229 6.79484Z" stroke="black" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M11.9929 6.79522C11.9929 7.8252 11.158 8.66017 10.128 8.66017C9.098 8.66017 8.26304 7.8252 8.26304 6.79522C8.26304 5.76524 9.098 4.93027 10.128 4.93027C11.158 4.93027 11.9929 5.76524 11.9929 6.79522Z" stroke="black" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">香港</span></a><a href="https://press.christies.com/section/regions/global" style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="26" height="26" viewbox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.2211 16.57L6.22116 16.57L6.21892 16.5647C5.88157 15.7673 5.81287 14.9508 6.01225 14.1073C6.21267 13.2594 6.60316 12.53 7.18437 11.9142C8.40538 10.921 9.12263 9.87932 9.26397 8.78395L9.26522 8.77423L9.26571 8.76444C9.30174 8.04389 9.04818 7.29968 8.54044 6.53808C8.03995 5.78734 7.48525 5.17216 6.87459 4.69719L6.7211 4.57782L6.56761 4.69719C3.86973 6.79555 2.51602 9.57033 2.51602 13C2.51602 14.732 2.90778 16.3583 3.69136 17.8755C4.47397 19.3907 5.53383 20.6186 6.8707 21.5544L7.26407 21.8298V21.3496C7.26407 19.9099 6.91273 18.3156 6.2211 16.57ZM8.86441 22.5511L8.85078 22.7284L9.01378 22.7995C10.3159 23.3671 11.7009 23.6504 13.1664 23.6504C16.0976 23.6504 18.6107 22.6066 20.6918 20.5254C22.773 18.4443 23.8168 15.9312 23.8168 13C23.8168 11