.6406 17.3558 16.7089 17.7444 15.9872C18.1342 15.2633 18.5321 14.7655 18.9305 14.4704L19.0316 14.3955V14.2695C19.0316 13.7351 19.0022 13.3236 18.9322 13.0576C18.9201 12.9212 18.8474 12.8098 18.7631 12.7256C18.6713 12.6337 18.5471 12.5544 18.4052 12.4834L18.3908 12.4763L18.3757 12.471L16.2761 11.7386ZM4.5053 4.33889C6.89985 1.94433 9.78224 0.75 13.1664 0.75C16.5506 0.75 19.433 1.94433 21.8275 4.33889C24.2221 6.73344 25.4164 9.61583 25.4164 13C25.4164 16.3842 24.2221 19.2666 21.8275 21.6611C19.433 24.0557 16.5506 25.25 13.1664 25.25C9.78224 25.25 6.89985 24.0557 4.5053 21.6611C2.11074 19.2666 0.916412 16.3842 0.916412 13C0.916412 9.61583 2.11074 6.73344 4.5053 4.33889Z" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"></path></svg><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">全球</span></a><a style="box-sizing: border-box;transition: 0.3s ease-in;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;outline: 0px;display: flex;color: rgb(57, 57, 57);flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center"><svg width="21" height="21" viewbox="0 0 21 21" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="0.5" y="1.80005" width="20" height="18.2" stroke="#8C1A11"></rect><path d="M0.675049 7.8125H20.3375" stroke="#8C1A11"></path><path d="M14.625 0L14.625 5" stroke="#8C1A11"></path><path d="M6.375 0L6.375 5" stroke="#8C1A11"></path><rect x="3.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="3.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="3.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="7.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="7.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="7.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="11.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="11.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="11.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="15.5" y="10" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="15.5" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect><rect x="15.5" y="16" width="2" height="2" fill="#8C1A11"></rect></svg><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0.5625rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: center; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0.6875rem; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">2024 年7月17日</span></a></p><p><br/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/43381739024435.jpg" width="594" height="321"/></p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">佳士得行政總裁施俊安表示：</span>&nbsp;</h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">「雖然佳士得的成交總額略為下降，但上半年的拍賣業務仍然穩定。面對充滿考驗的宏觀經濟環境，</em></span></h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">我們維持並提高</em></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">衡量業績表現的各項關鍵指標。」</em></span></h2><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">&nbsp;</em></h2><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>美元21億 拍賣成交總額&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">去年同期為美元</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">27</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">億</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">)</em></p></li><li><p>87%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;成交比率&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">去年同期為</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">87%</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">)</em></p></li><li><p>111%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 落搥價總額與低估價的比率&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">去年同期為</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">107%</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">)</em></p></li><li><p>82%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 網上競投&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">去年同期為</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">79%</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">)</em></p></li><li><p>六件&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 全球10件最高成交價藝術品當中，六件由佳士得拍出&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">去年同期為四件</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">)</em></p></li><li><p>29%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 客戶為千禧世代和Z世代&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">去年同期為</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">29%</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">)</em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p></li></ul><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>所有地區的私人洽購均表現強勁，並吸引新買家參與</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">展望未來，夏季及其後的重點活動：</span></p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>香港：佳士得將於今年9月在The Henderson開設佔地50,000平方呎的全新亞太區總部，並於9月26及27日呈獻二十及二十一世紀藝術開幕拍賣，隨後於10月舉辦雅逸精品拍賣，11月則舉辦亞洲藝術拍賣。</p></li><li><p>倫敦：「Ahmed Mater: Chronicles」展覽展出沙地阿拉伯藝術家哈邁德馬特 (Ahmed Mater) 借出的作品，包括攝影作品、影片、繪畫、雕塑和藝術裝置，將於7月18日開幕，展期至8月22日。</p></li><li><p>紐約：來自已故慈善家兼微軟聯合創辦人保羅艾倫 (Paul G. Allen) 的「Gen One：保羅·艾倫珍藏創新傑作」系列拍賣，頌揚開創性的第一代科技及其背後的創新先驅。系列包含兩場網上拍賣和9月12日舉行的現場拍賣。</p></li><li><p>巴黎：亨利德·圖盧茲-勞特累克 (Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec) 的《簡·艾薇兒身處日本咖啡館》（1892年作），將於10月18日在巴黎舉行的二十及二十一世紀藝術旗艦拍賣「前衛浪潮呈獻意大利思潮」中矚目亮相。</p></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">2024&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">年初至今</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">在充滿挑戰的宏觀經濟環境下，佳士得於2024年上半年取得美元21億的全球拍賣成交總額，期內全球最高成交價的10件藝術品當中，佳士得拍出六件，同時呈獻六個重要珍藏，拍賣成交比率為87%，落搥價總額為低估價111%，彰顯佳士得隱固的市場領導地位。踏入下半年，佳士得已在倫敦拍場以超過美元1,300萬拍出兩件刷新紀錄的古典大師作品，並宣布將於9月在紐約舉辦創新的系列拍賣，呈獻保羅·艾倫的珍藏傑作，以及公布在巴黎、倫敦、紐約及香港舉辦大型二十及二十一世紀藝術拍賣的計劃，令人期待。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">2024</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">年上半年全球拍賣數據</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1