 width="60" height="47"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 91.4538px; font-size: 11pt !important; text-transform: inherit !important; line-height: 1.35em !important;">古典大師</p></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 15px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-transform: inherit !important;" width="60" height="47"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 100.041px; font-size: 11pt !important; text-transform: inherit !important; line-height: 1.35em !important;">美元7,700萬</p></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 15px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-transform: inherit !important;" width="60" height="47"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 105.462px; font-size: 11pt !important; text-transform: inherit !important; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">(32%)</em></p></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 389.565px; height: 47.5694px; text-transform: inherit !important;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 15px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-transform: inherit !important;" width="60" height="47"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 91.4538px; font-size: 1