; font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 20px; touch-action: manipulation; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); transition-duration: 0.15s; transition-property: color; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.39, 0.58, 0.57, 1); text-wrap: wrap;">註冊在未來拍賣會上出價</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-size: 20px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">的更多資訊，請訪問&nbsp;</span><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://goodingco.com/" target="_blank" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 20px; touch-action: manipulation; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); transition-duration: 0.15s; transition-property: color; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.39, 0.58, 0.57, 1); text-wrap: wrap;">goodingco.com</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-size: 20px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">。</span></p><p><br/></p><h2 class="chr-heading-l-serif mt-5 mb-5" _msttexthash="119432352" _msthash="29" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 3rem; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 24px !important; margin-bottom: 24px !important;">想買一輛收藏車？Gooding Christie&#39;s 為您答疑解惑</h2><p class="chr-rich-text__body" _msttexthash="1192982206" _msthash="30" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.4; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">從哪裡開始，尋找什麼以及 Gooding Christie&#39;s 的更多專家提示。這家首屈一指的汽車拍賣行目前保持著眾多品牌的世界紀錄，包括法拉利、保時捷、邁凱輪和布加迪</p><p><a href="https://www.christies.com.cn/stories/collector-car-guide-gooding-christies-f1cbdafb19674062835e6b0719a0f628" class="chr-button chr-button--primary chr-button--lg chr-button--light" target="" data-track="|corporate:flexible editorial component:Read now" _msttexthash="14208454" _msthash="31" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: none; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; touch-action: manipulation; background-color: hsl(var(--c-dominant)); text-decoration-line: none; text-transform: uppercase; transition-duration: 0.15s; transition-property: color, background-color, border-color, box-shadow, -webkit-box-shadow; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.39, 0.58, 0.57, 1); cursor: pointer; border-radius: 2px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; text-wrap: nowrap;">立即閱讀</a></p><p><br/></p>','1');
