INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('67','22','市場觀察 | 2025年亞洲首場拍賣 | 印尼藝術收藏價值最高 東南亞藝術迎來新高潮','','亞洲藝術','','1','2025年亞洲的第一場藝術拍賣，1月18日在新加坡落下帷幕。2025年新加坡藝術週期間，蘇富比現當代藝術拍賣與藝博會ART SG、S.E.A.Focus同期在獅城展開，而與封閉交易的藝博會相比，公開競拍的藝術拍賣會，對藝術市場風向更具標誌性意義。亞洲藝術市場經歷了低迷的2024年後，在2025年元旦剛過、春節將至的寒冷1月，在溫暖的熱帶島嶼拉開帷幕，為新一年的藝術市場打頭陣。| 不再對西方藝術盲目&hellip;','1741076885','1741076885','<p><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/38321741076831.png" width="740" height="740"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: wfont_f32af7_03b1017063434e02b8f377b473db8064, wf_03b1017063434e02b8f377b47, orig_genyomin_jp_semibold; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2025年亞洲的第一場藝術拍賣，1月18日在新加坡落下帷幕。2025年新加坡藝術週期間，蘇富比現當代藝術拍賣與藝博會ART SG、S.E.A.Focus同期在獅城展開，而與封閉交易的藝博會相比，公開競拍的藝術拍賣會，對藝術市場風向更具標誌性意義。亞洲藝術市場經歷了低迷的2024年後，在2025年元旦剛過、春節將至的寒冷1月，在溫暖的熱帶島嶼拉開帷幕，為新一年的藝術市場打頭陣。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: wfont_f32af7_03b1017063434e02b8f377b473db8064, wf_03b1017063434e02b8f377b47, orig_genyomin_jp_semibold; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-r5fyi3858" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">| 不再對西方藝術盲目崇拜</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-d7uzf3860" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-d751k3862" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">在1月14-17日為期四天的預展中，備受矚目的前5位「最貴」藝術品中，兩件都是西方藝術品，分別是第一貴的估值高達2640萬港幣（470萬新幣）的美國當代藝術家馬克·布拉福德（Mark Bradford）的《洛杉磯》（L.A），和第三貴的估值1500萬港幣（270萬新幣）的印象派藝術家夏加爾的《圍著果籃共舞》。</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-s2mt33864" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-wcq4v3866" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">拍賣結果卻出人意料，兩件估值Top 1和Top 3的作品均陷入流拍的尷尬處境。如果去年9月香港佳士得秋拍尚有瑞士藏家給印象派硬通貨「救場」，新加坡的這場拍賣就再無人「下場救市」，表明以新加坡為代表的東南亞藏家們，與以香港為代表的亞洲藏家一樣，對港幣千萬級的天價西方藝術品不再感冒和盲目跟風，對其巨額成本和投資回報率不再看好。除昂貴的西方藝術外，像村上隆這樣的大牌藝術家，也不再被市場追捧，估價不到百萬港幣的（8.5-17萬新幣，約48-95萬港幣）的《花：靈魂之交》無人接盤，進入流拍。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: wfont_f32af7_03b1017063434e02b8f377b473db8064, wf_03b1017063434e02b8f377b47, orig_genyomin_jp_semibold; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: wfont_f32af7_03b1017063434e02b8f377b473db8064, wf_03b1017063434e02b8f377b47, orig_genyomin_jp_semibold; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/40661741076832.png" width="740" height="740"/></span></p><p><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/84421741076834.png" width="740" height="740"/></p><p><br/></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-pdjyn3870" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">| 東南亞最貴藝術家誕生，印尼藝術價值最高</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-7nqzj3872" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: initial; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX w1bOB R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-72ej73874" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">相反，東南亞本土藝術的價值被藏家十分看好，回歸本土、支持本土藝術的趨勢，在東南亞更為明顯。本場最高成交額前5的作品，有4件都是東南亞藝術。印尼當代女性藝術家克里絲汀·艾珠（Christine Ay Tjoe）是全場最高價藝術家，拍賣打破了克里絲汀·艾珠2017年在香港富藝斯拍賣行1,170萬港幣的最高銷售記錄，她的《層疊之光》（Lights for the Layer），以1652萬港幣（294萬新幣）拔得頭籌，是全場最高價，也是藝術家迄今最高記錄。她的另一件作品《水準溜溜球》（Horizontal Yoyo）也以最高估值160%的高溢價賣出，323萬港幣（57.6萬新幣）的交易額排當晚拍賣第6位。克里絲汀·艾珠今年52歲，來自印尼萬隆，致力於抽象表現主義藝術創作，曾在萬隆理工學院美術系學習，曾做個時裝設計師，是20世紀90年代崛起的印尼藝術家之一，也是東南亞最炙手可熱的當代藝術明星。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/55571741076838.png" width="740" height="740"/></p><p><img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4c1fe5_91e749726653481da8f1919548f1e02b~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_740,h_740,al_c,q_90,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/4c1fe5_91e749726653481da8f1919548f1e02b~mv2.png" width="740" height="740"/></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX w1bOB R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-lui2a5152" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font-style: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-style,unset); font-variant: inherit; font-weight: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-weight,unset); font-stretch: inherit; font-size: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-size,unset); line-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-line-height,unset); font-family: var(--ricos-custom-p-font-family,unset); font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--ricos-custom-p-color,unset); min-height: var(--ricos-custom-p-min-height,unset); text-decoration: var(--ricos-custom-p-text-decoration,unset); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span class="iAaUR" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: var(--ricos-custom-p-background-color,unset); border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">不過，整場拍賣中最受矚目的作品，其實是有東南亞現代藝術奠基人之稱的印尼現代藝術鼻祖拉登·薩勒（Raden Syarif Bustaman Saleh）的兩幅爪哇島風景油畫《默巴布與默拉皮火山景觀》（Landscape: View of Merbabu and Merapi）和《塔拉加博達斯火山景觀》（Landscape: View of Talagabodas）。作於1862年的油畫《默巴布與默拉皮火山景觀》以1146萬港幣（204萬新幣）出售，是全場第二高價拍品；另一件《塔拉加博達斯火山景觀》以最高估值2.3倍的溢價賣出364萬港幣（64.8萬新幣），位居全場第4。拉登·薩勒是印尼國寶級繪畫大師，他的作品也是新加坡國家博物館的鎮館之寶，是新加坡國家博物館永久展覽《宣示與夢想：19世紀以來的東南亞藝術》的開山之作。他是第一位進入荷蘭王室的荷屬東印度肖像畫家，以歐洲王室貴族肖像畫，和爪哇島巡獵與野生動物主題作品聞名。</span></span></p><p class="Lrhnp ZqyaX UxJLO R4K5w" dir="auto" id="viewer-8vgo43880" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-