mily: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《救世主》尚未修復前狀態。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在莫德斯蒂尼的修復紀錄中，我們若是仔細比較加奈與達文西的版本，便可以從達文西的《救世主》在畫作中的染色效果更近似於《蒙娜麗莎》和《聖約翰》的細膩感，這類特徵在其他同題材的複製品中是沒有出現過的，儘管這幅作品曾經歷非常嚴重的損毀與漫長修復過程，在修復報告中我們仍可以看到，她認為該畫作在眼睛磨損的部分特別難處理，因為它們並不是以一般的油畫上色方式呈現，而是透過薄質的釉料直接塗於白色的打底層上，幾乎沒有使用任何厚重的色彩，這種技法更接近水彩。後續也對這幅畫作進行了X光的測試，斷定該作品使用的木材是核桃木，這也與達文西同一時期創作的《聖約翰》使用的木材相同，因此加深了它為真跡的推測。而莫德斯蒂尼最終透過最低限的修改，使面目全非的作品成為了現今我們所見的完整樣貌。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/3291741084342.jpg" width="450" height="568"/></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《救世主》作品修復細節。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">由於達文西現存已知的作品僅有15幅，而這件《救世主》的宗教題材更是加深了外界對於這件作品是否為真跡的探討與期待。2005年這幅畫作以1萬美元的價格被一個美國藝術經銷商收購並進行了修復。到了2013年它被巴黎一位經銷商伊夫．布維爾（Yves Bouvier）購買，隨後又由俄羅斯富豪翁德米特里．雷波洛夫列夫（Dmitry Rybolovlev）以1.27億美元收藏，之後委託給佳士得拍賣會進行2017年的拍賣。儘管最終這幅畫作經過多位專家的反覆研究形成了共識，只不過一旦它再度出現於世人眼前時，不同看法和意見必然仍會持續的圍繞於這件大師作品。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('82','22','拍賣會常勝軍葛飾北齋〈神奈川沖浪裏〉九月現身佳士得，是否能再次為低迷的藝術市場帶來新活水？','','藝術品','','1','紐約佳士得拍賣會
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('83','22','曾在佳士得以NFT作品拍下20億台幣震撼藝術圈的 Beeple，將於南京迎來全球首場個展','','藝術品','','1','2021年正值 NFT 風靡全球之時，美國數位藝術家Beeple（本名Mike Winkelmann）當時以作品《每一天》（Everydays－The First 5000 Days）在佳士得拍出69,346,250美元，相當於台幣20億的高價，對於一個沒有畫廊代理、沒有展覽紀錄、拍賣紀錄的藝術家，無疑為藝術圈投擲出一枚震撼彈。而佳士得也破天荒地成為當年首間拍賣 NFT 藝術品的拍賣公司，並以Be&hellip;','1741084858','1741084858','<p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">2021年正值 NFT 風靡全球之時，美國數位藝術家Beeple（本名Mike Winkelmann）當時以作品《每一天》（Everydays－The First 5000 Days）在佳士得拍出69,346,250美元，相當於台幣20億的高價，對於一個沒有畫廊代理、沒有展覽紀錄、拍賣紀錄的藝術家，無疑為藝術圈投擲出一枚震撼彈。而佳士得也破天荒地成為當年首間拍賣 NFT 藝術品的拍賣公司，並以Beeple領銜，使他一夕之間成為位居最昂貴的在世藝術家之一，亦為NFT在藝術拍賣市場寫下歷史新頁。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">如今，這位曾經因為創下NFT歷史紀錄而轟動一時的Beeple，將於南京德基藝術博物館迎來全球首場個人大展「Beeple：來自人造未來的故事」（Beeple: Tales From A Synthetic Future）於 2024 年 11 月 14 日（星期四）重磅啟幕。展覽由當代藝術界頂尖國際策展人、藝評家兼藝術史學家 Hans Ulrich Obrist 作為藝術顧問與德基藝術博物館攜手，系統而全面地回顧 Beeple 的藝術生涯，邀請觀眾以沉浸的方式，探索 Beeple 藝術實踐中的多重維度，了解其對於數位藝術及當代藝術史發展所提出的詰問及帶來的影響。此次為全球迄今規模最大的 Beeple 個人展覽，涵蓋其藝術生涯中最矚目的作品，包括《每一天》、 《人類一號》、《S.2122》，以及為本次展覽特別創作的全新作品等，同時還將呈現致力發掘培養年輕數位藝術家的徵集與展示單元，以及一系列座談會與公眾項目。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">Hans Ulrich Obrist 表示：「Beeple 透過對新媒體和 NFT 的實驗，在藝術、音樂和技術領域獲得了全球認可。他的作品融合了上述眾多領域，「Beeple：來自人造未來的故事」展覽將全方位、多維度地呈現藝術家的創作實踐。這場沉浸式展覽是過去、現在和未來現實框架之間的碰撞，體現 Beeple 的跨學科創作方法。展覽將呈現他藝術實踐的發展歷程，包括廣為人知的《每一天》系列開始，從手繪圖像到數位渲染繪畫，再到他最近的動態藝術作品：由錄像和三維雕塑組成的生物體。展覽還將重現藝術家位於北卡羅來納州查爾斯頓工作室的元素，再現藝術家經由計算機技術或『數位考古』創作的幾個早期項目，為觀眾提供對藝術家多年創作過程的獨特解讀視角。本次展覽將以時間順序呈現，展示 Beeple 眾多作品中共存但各異的時間性，講述繪畫和塗鴉等低科技含量的方式或模擬創作模式如何繼續作為他極具前瞻性的數位實踐的重要基礎。」</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p></p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">Beeple重要作品匯聚！</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《每一天》是對自律、創造力和藝術成長不懈追求的持續探索。自 2007 年開始，Beeple 每天都會創作一件全新的藝術作品，迄今已經創作超過 6000 件，並且還在不斷增加——每一天的創作都是捕捉當下時代精神的視覺日記，整個過程亦是藝術家對於自身技能和想象力界限的不斷突破。Beeple 的作品經常將超現實主義與高度寫實主義融合在一起，在未來的奇異場景中推演當下的事件，反映了數位時代的混亂和反烏托邦性質。本次展覽將在藝術家《每一天》系列的 6000 多件作品中，精選部分作品進行展出。</p><p><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/87581741084847.jpg" width="500" height="625"/></p><p><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/39521741084848.jpg" width="500" height="625"/></p><p><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/77551741084848.jpg" width="500" height="625"/></p><p></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在《人類一號》中，Beeple 首次賦予其作品能夠隨着時間動態變化的獨特性，用前所未有的方式充分挖掘數位藝術媒介的潛力。傳統藝術作品如同有限的陳述，在完成的那一刻就凍結在時間中；然而《人類一號》實體雕塑中的內容可以遠程更改，使其擁有了生物體般的生長性，藝術家可以隨着時間的推移不斷添加新的意義和內容，更像是一場持續的對話。《人類一號》描繪了虛擬人物的旅程，這件作品本身也是一場旅程，而它的終點通向何方，甚至對 Beeple 來說都是尚未可知的。</span></span></span><br/></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/40631741084849.jpg" width="500" height="243"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/50111741084849.jpg" width="500" height="746"/></span></span></span></p><p></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《S.2122》是 Beeple 對於 2122 年人類未來圖景的設想，在一個逾兩米高的旋轉矩形雕塑內，一座獨立的多單元高層建築矗立於未來主義的海洋環境中。《S.2122》亦是藝術家首次將過往重要作品聚合於同一件實體雕塑中呈現，囊括了《每一天》系列的經典元素以及《人類一號》中的宇航員形象。這件作品同樣具備可生長的特性，作品里的內容會持續更新——海洋水位會不斷上升，建築中的人類也會隨之展開應對。透過這件作品，Beeple 表達了對於未來以及技術在塑造世界中的作用的持續迷戀，不僅展現了氣候問題的嚴重性，也展現了人類生存的堅強意志和力量。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/4011741084849.jpg" width="500" height="746"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">德基藝術博物館館長艾琳表示：「作為一種嚴肅且不斷演變的藝術表達形式，數位藝術是當代藝術發展的重要里程碑。Beeple 創作中所探討的議題深受快速變化的時代、人性與技術之間常常令人困惑的交集的影響，與德基藝術博物館所關注的人類生活、技術、自然、宇宙之間變化和締聯的議題相契合。而他對於每一個當下的積極回應，以及持續透過前沿的創作工具生成自身特有的藝術表達，使其成為了數位藝術領域獨具代表性的研究樣本。藉由鼓勵公眾介入技術更迭的背景之下藝術創作與欣賞方式所經歷的變遷歷程，以期形成關於數位藝術的廣泛認知，亦對數位時代藝術家的意義展開持續探索。」</span></span></span></span></span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">展覽啟幕的同時，還將為年輕數位藝術家提供作品展示的平台，同步呈現來自全球的優秀創意力量，並透過一系列座談會與公眾項目，以更多元化的議題、更開放的介入形式，進一步探索數位藝術發展的潛力，突破數位藝術的可能性界限。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">藝術家 Beeple 表示：「很高興我的全球首場個人展覽即將在中國南京舉辦，非常榮幸也非常期待，能夠在這樣一座融匯深厚文化底蘊與現代創新力量的城市展出我的作品。此次透過與德基藝術博物館、Hans Ulrich Obrist 先生共同合作，集中呈現我藝術生涯最重要、最具代表性的作品——包括《每一天》系列精選、《人類一號》、《S.2122》等數位雕塑，以及特別為本次展覽創作的全新作品。這次個展是我藝術生涯的重要里程碑，更是對於未來可能性的探索，是連接我藝術旅程的過去、未來的關鍵時刻。另外，非常開心能夠在展覽同期加入徵集與展示的部分，這對於發掘、培養數位藝術領域的年輕人才非常重要，相信我們能夠引發更多有意義的對話，創造前所未有的藝術世界。」</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="http://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/42391741084850.jpg" width="500" height="704"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p></p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">關於 Beeple</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">Beeple 本名邁克·溫克爾曼（Mike Winkelmann），為數位藝術家及設計師，其作品融合了社會環境、流行文化與科幻小說，常以挑釁或諷刺的口吻對新聞及互聯網文化做出回應，實時遠程修改作品的圖像和敘事。Beeple 因其連續性的作品系列《每一天》而備受矚目，該系列自 2007 年持續至今，他每天都會創作一幅獨特作品並將其上傳至網絡，從未間斷。Beeple 的雕塑作品喚起一種獨特的疆域，與從希臘化時代到網絡時代的世界產生共鳴。透過向數位藝術的豐富歷史致敬，思索人類和媒體未來的影像，突破人們關於新興技術的幻想，拓寬數位與物理存在之間的模糊邊界。</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">關於德基藝術博物館</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">德基藝術博物館立足中國南京，依託德基集團近三十年有序收藏，逐步融匯中國古代、金陵在地性、中國及國際現當代三大方向，構建豐富多元的館藏、研究與展覽體系，於 2017 年正式面向公眾開放。基於自身特性，博物館力圖跨越文化與時代的邊界，介入不同時期的歷史圖景，回應全球藝術進程的變化發展，將南京置身於世界藝術交流的前沿現場，推動中國、 亞洲和國際之間的來往與聯結，為公眾呈現獨特的藝術文化體驗。</p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"></span></p><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"></span></span></span></span></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('84','22','中國藝術史（1）','','藝術品','','1','人物畫【代表性藝術家】陳洪綬(1598~1652):《稀髮圖冊》《歸來圖》崔子忠(?~1644):《長白仙跡圖》《雲中玉女圖》曾鯨(1568~1650):《葛一龍像》《王時敏像》【起源】明代人物畫，略比元代為振興。然多模擬唐宋人舊派，不如隋唐之輝煌，照耀百世，其中以仇英，精於摹古，曾隨周臣學畫，並廣泛師法唐宋大家，創精麗艷逸之史實風俗畫，自成一格。明代中後期繪畫出現漸趨僵滯又轉換生機、尊崇與創造並&hellip;','1741356236','1741356236','<h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 33px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">人物畫</h1><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【代表性藝術家】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳洪綬(1598~1652):《稀髮圖冊》《歸來圖》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">崔子忠(?~1644):《長白仙跡圖》《雲中玉女圖》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">曾鯨(1568~1650):《葛一龍像》《王時敏像》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【起源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">明代人物畫，略比元代為振興。然多模擬唐宋人舊派，不如隋唐之輝煌，照耀百世，其中以仇英，精於摹古，曾隨周臣學畫，並廣泛師法唐宋大家，創精麗艷逸之史實風俗畫，自成一格。明代中後期繪畫出現漸趨僵滯又轉換生機、尊崇與創造並存的局面。山水畫經過“吳門”後生們的耕耘和追隨漸趨平穩；花鳥畫在陳淳、徐渭等畫師的開拓下，顯示出勃然生機。陳洪綬、崔子忠和曾鯨又使人物肖像畫在畫壇上大放異彩，深刻影響著後世。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【風格】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳洪綬擅長人物、花鳥、山水，繪畫藝術中數量最多、最有特色的是版畫人物，如《西廂記》、《九歌圖》等，除了版畫之外，流傳至今不少人物畫作品多為明亡以後所作，其筆下的人物往往經過大膽的誇張變形，相貌危岸奇峭，形象上擅長利用誇大個性和襯托對比手法。用筆簡括，人物誇張變形，然而風神逼真生動，他的畫風對後世影響深遠。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">其子陳宇、弟子嚴湛、魏湘等直承其法，清代王樹穀、華嵒、羅聘等都融入他的畫法，清末“四任”(任熊﹑任頤﹑任薰﹑任預)更進一步發揚其畫風。崔子忠善畫人物、仕女，兼工肖像畫，師法南唐周文矩，衣紋多屈曲轉折，筆墨清麗，與陳洪綬並稱“南陳北崔”。丁雲鵬善畫道釋人物，畫風雖與陳洪綬不同，但都反應明末清初書畫藝術上的一股“寧拙勿巧、寧醜勿媚”的風尚。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【後續】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在陳洪綬、崔子忠創作活躍期，另一位大師曾鯨在肖像畫方面擁有令人矚目的成就，畫重墨骨，即在用淡線勾出輪廓五官後和以淡墨渲染出明暗凹凸。如鏡取影，形象逼真，這種畫法較富立體感，可能已受到當時新傳入的西洋畫法的一定啟發。學者甚眾，遂形成“波臣派”，影響直至清代。陳洪綬、崔子忠等人的人物畫，著重造型上創新面貌，有人稱之為「變成主義」的畫風，也給陳陳相因的臨摹習尚注入一點新生命。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【延伸閱讀】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">網路:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">明代之道釋人物畫</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">https://market.cloud.edu.tw/content/senior/art/tp_cc/ink/ca72.htm</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">歷代中國傳統人物畫源流概說</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">http://www.deng-fen.com/references/figure_painting/</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【圖源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%99%88%E6%B4%AA%E7%BB%B6#/media/File:Chen_hongshou_selfportrait,1635_-_crop.jpg </span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 33px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;">山水畫(一)</span><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;">【代表性藝術家】</span></p><p><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">李思訓(651～716):《江帆樓閣圖》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">李昭道(生卒年不詳):《明皇幸蜀圖》《春山行旅圖》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">王維(701～761):《雪溪圖》《輞川圖》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【起源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">政治統一與社會經濟繁榮的境況，為唐代寫下繪畫成就輝煌的史頁。透過儒、佛、道三教並立發展的社會思想，唐代山水畫除了持續魏晉以來發展，表現技法已漸趨完備之外，青綠山水與水墨山水的興起也豐富了民族藝術傳統。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【風格】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">青綠山水:初唐李思訓繼承展子虔的風格技法，以細緻工筆的「界畫」確立了「青綠山水」一派。對於樹木的描繪著重以簡單的皴筆勾勒交叉，用色以青綠顏色為主，有時並以金粉加重轉折處，藉以產生金碧輝煌的亮麗效果。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">水墨山水:水墨山水的藝術形式確立於盛唐時期的吳道子，以追求嚮往平淡自然的老莊哲學，開啟破墨山水的審美境界。王維則進一步開拓水墨技巧，並首先創立「禪境」的表現，在詩與畫結合的山水畫之間，實現天人合一的美學境界。以用筆的乾濕調和濃淡暈染，以及使用簡單的勾皴法表現山水之間的詩情畫意。至中晚唐時期，王維的水墨渲染則在王洽的「潑墨」技法中得到進一步的自由發展。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【後續】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">唐代王維的畫以「畫中有詩、詩中有畫」著稱，影響了後世對於意境營造的最高要求，成為山水畫創作的重要的課題之一。中國的山水畫並以老莊哲學為基礎，形成於玄學風氣盛行之中，玄遠的藝術觀至此確立了一千多年來中國山水畫的基本方向，並成一獨立的體系。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 