: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">【圖說】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《羅浮宮方院西牆上的雕刻》／Jean Goujon, Image from</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 4px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">http://vr.theatre.ntu.edu.tw/fineart/sculpture-wt/goujon/goujon.htm</span></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('90','22','西洋藝術史（3）','','藝術品','','1','義大利藝術（17th-18th）【代表藝術家】安‧卡拉西（Annibale Carracci,1560~1609）：《梳妝的維納斯》、《聖母哀悼基督之死》雷涅（Guido Reni,1575~1642）：《黎明女神奧羅拉》卡拉瓦喬（Michelangelo Merisi da Caravaggio,1573~1610）：《聖馬太的召喚》、《聖多馬的懷疑》貝爾尼尼（Gianlorenzo Berni…','1741357511','1741357524','<h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 33px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">義大利藝術（17th-18th）</h1><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【代表藝術家】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">安‧卡拉西（Annibale Carracci,1560~1609）：《梳妝的維納斯》、《聖母哀悼基督之死》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">雷涅（Guido Reni,1575~1642）：《黎明女神奧羅拉》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">卡拉瓦喬（Michelangelo Merisi da Caravaggio,1573~1610）：《聖馬太的召喚》、《聖多馬的懷疑》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">貝爾尼尼（Gianlorenzo Bernini,1598~1680）：《聖德蕾莎祭壇》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【起源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">16世紀中葉以來，義大利藝術中的矯飾主義也不過是一個短暫的過渡。15世紀末期後，歐洲各國不斷拓展科學新知，產生許多發明的新科技。因地理上新航線大發現，造成大量的通商和殖民的興盛，生活物質越來越富有，也開始有自由思想的觀念。而在義大利南歐等舊教盛行的國家，以宮廷和教會為中心，主要表揚彰顯舊教榮耀、華麗的藝術、誇耀王權聲威，在反宗教改革情形下，巴洛克藝術興起。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【風格】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">巴洛克藝術的風格，主要承襲自文藝復興的矯飾主義，著重在強烈感情的表現，無論在精神上和手法上與古典藝術都大相逕庭。巴洛克(Baroque)一詞源出於葡萄牙語“barroco”一詞，意為不合常規，指一種形狀不圓有瑕疵的珍珠，則後為批評家用來反對十七世紀潮流的，這種帶貶義的稱呼，用以區別十七世紀不同於盛期文藝復興的藝術風格。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">巴洛克風格強調流動感、戲劇性、誇張性等特點，常採用富於動態感的造型要素，如曲線、斜線等。在建築上，裝飾華麗，古典的樣式和曲面、曲線倂用，注重建築物四周景觀，有廣場、庭園、噴泉、雕像等，追求結構複雜多變的建築，配以大量雕塑和裝飾的效果。繪畫和雕塑上，對光線與色彩的強調，廣泛使用對角線、弧線、曲線等富有運動與戲劇性的構圖結構。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【後續】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">當16世紀義大利矯飾主義風格盛行，卡拉西及追隨者力圖使文藝復興的古典美原則發揚光大，他們結合文藝復興大師的藝術，再加上通過寫生而達到一種自然的風格。另一方面，16世紀末至17世紀初的義大利，出現了另一位與卡拉西風格截然不同的藝術家卡拉瓦喬，他重視描寫眼見的真實，忠誠的描寫生活中平凡的或下層生活中的普通人物形象。在雕塑方面，巴洛克大師貝爾尼尼風格具有動感及戲劇性，他的作品將建築、繪畫、雕塑融為一體，為藝術創作開創新意。然而，18世紀獨佔地位的義大利藝術已遠不及法國，從此法國成為藝術發展的先鋒。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【延伸閱讀】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">書:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">沈瑩(譯) (2007)。文藝復興與巴洛克。上海:人民出版社。(海因里希‧沃爾夫林)</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">張心龍(1997)。巴洛克之旅。台北: 雄獅美術。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">陳英德、張彌彌(2005)。世界名畫家全集─卡拉瓦喬。台北:藝術家。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">董強、曹勝操(譯)(2003)。古典主義與巴洛克藝術。台北: 閣林。(皮耶．卡巴納)</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">網路:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《每日頭條》如何區分「巴洛克」與「洛可可」？</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">https://kknews.cc/zh-tw/culture/8eo6g8e.html</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《維基百科：西西里巴洛克》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E8%A5%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E6%B4%9B%E5%85%8B</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《視覺素養學習網：貝尼尼》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">http://vr.theatre.ntu.edu.tw/fineart/sculpture-wt/bernini/bernini.htm</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《維基百科：卡拉瓦喬》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8D%A1%E6%8B%89%E7%93%A6%E4%B9%94</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【圖說】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《聖彼得受難》／ Michelangelo Merisi da Caravaggio, Image by</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%A1%E6%8B%89%E7%93%A6%E4%B9%94 </span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 33px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">17th法蘭德斯藝術</h1><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【代表藝術家】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">魯本斯(Peter Paul Rubens,1577~1640):《劫奪呂西普的女兒》《下十字架》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">凡戴克(A Van Dyck,1599~1641):《英格蘭王查理一世》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【起源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">16世紀尼德蘭發生革命，數十年的爭鬥後分南北兩方。北為荷蘭聯省共和國，南為西班牙天主教會和封建專制下所控制，而改稱法蘭德斯，大約為現今地理位置上的比利時。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【風格】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">法蘭德斯為西歐的一個歷史地名，泛指古代尼德蘭南部地區，大體上包括現在的比利時、盧森堡以及法國東北的部分地區。其藝術史最重要的期間是從十五世紀到十八世紀；其中又以十七世紀為黃金時代。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">17世紀法蘭德斯最偉大的藝術家是魯本斯，也是法蘭德斯最具巴洛克藝術家風格的畫家。他創造出誇張的形體、多變的線條、鮮明的色彩、瀟灑的筆觸、細膩的刻畫，融入義大利藝術的優雅與自己的風格結合，讓作品帶有很強的感染力。承繼魯本斯的是他的學生凡戴克，他受到英王查理一世和貴族們的賞識，成為查理一世的宮廷畫師。從他的作品可了解當時英國貴族優雅無比、權勢穩固、文化水準高的人物、神聖王權維護者，顯示出被理想化的英國上流社會。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【後續】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">魯本斯的油畫技法為直接上色，一次完成法，揮筆倉狂，色彩鮮明，用色大膽，強烈明暗，勃發生命活力，筆下的男女幼童人物全都是生動活潑，充滿活力，似乎有心跳和呼吸般，對十九世紀法國浪漫派繪畫，有著直接且深遠的影響力。凡戴克則擅長肖像畫，對英國繪畫發展有深遠的影響。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【延伸閱讀】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">書:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">何政廣(1999)。魯本斯:巴洛克繪畫大師。台北:藝術家。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">胡永芬(2001)。巴洛克天才:魯本斯。台北:閣林國際。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">胡永芬(2001)。永恆的肖像:范.戴克。台北:閣林國際。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">網路:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">第 28 講《荷蘭與法蘭德斯的巴洛克藝術》 http://vr.theatre.ntu.edu.tw/fineart/th9_1000/open-28-broadcast.htm</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">大紀元文化網http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/1/8/30/c4487.htm</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">魯本斯http://vr.theatre.ntu.edu.tw/fineart/painter-wt/rubens/rubens.htm</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">維基百科 安東尼•凡•戴克http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%9C%E5%B0%BC%C2%B7%E5%87%A1%C2%B7%E6%88%B4%E5%85%8B</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【圖說】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《劫奪留西帕斯的女兒》, Peter Paul Rubens, Image from https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%C2%B7%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%C2%B7%E9%AD%AF%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%AF </span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 33px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">17th荷蘭藝術</h1><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【代表藝術家】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">弗朗斯‧哈爾斯(F Hals,1580~1666) :《吉普賽女郎》《哈萊姆養老院的女管理員》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">林布蘭特(Rembrandt van Rijn,1606~1669):《杜普教授的解剖課》《夜警》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">維梅爾(Jan Vermeer van Delft,1632~1675):《倒牛奶的女僕》《畫室》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【起源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">17世紀初，荷蘭獲得獨立權，成為歐洲最早的資本主義國家。17世紀中葉為荷蘭的鼎盛期，經濟文化繁盛，開始定期出版文物刊物與報紙。而反對專制統治和天主教的荷蘭，信仰新教，獲得更多的言論與思想自由。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">雖然他們生活簡樸，需刻苦耐勞工作，但荷蘭人並不喜歡法蘭德斯的豪華風，也反對巴洛克風情。藝術，並非再是宮廷與貴族為主角，而慢慢轉向平民風俗畫。他們喜愛忠實於生活，描繪市民日常生活和風俗習慣，作品漸由大轉小，成小巧適合在家庭中陳列的畫幅。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【風格】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">此時的畫家，由於受尼德蘭藝術家影響，描繪的題材較專一，開始出現各種類別的分類畫家，如風景畫、肖像畫、靜物、風俗畫等。將畫分類別、畫幅小巧的繪畫風格稱「荷蘭小畫派」，其最有名為維梅爾，其大多數的畫都是描寫典型的荷蘭家庭中一景，大多是夾有人物的靜物畫，他喜愛畫光經由窗戶而入射室內的柔美光。而以肖像畫著稱的有哈爾斯，他觀察人民生活細微，可以立即補捉到主角在一瞬間的特殊神情，富有感染力的描繪風格，是此時期肖像畫最為成功的一位。寫實派大師為林布蘭特，他因受到卡拉瓦喬寫實藝術的影響而成為荷蘭最有名的寫實派畫家。擅長於宗教畫、肖像畫、風景畫、風俗畫、及版畫，曾畫近數百幅的自畫像，累積早年到晚年的自我肖像作品。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【延伸閱讀】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">書:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">人民美術出版社(2009)。維米爾。上海:人民美術出版社。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">花亦芬(2008)。林布蘭特與聖經─荷蘭黃金時代藝術與宗教的對話。台北:三民。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">黃珮玲(1995)。林布蘭。台北:遠流。(ChristopherWhite)</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">網路:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">十七世紀荷蘭繪畫的主題—維梅爾生活的時代http://life.fhl.net/Art/vermeer/02.htm</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">維基百科荷蘭黃金時代http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【圖說】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《夜巡》, Rembrandt Harmenszoon van Rijn, Image from</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">http://www.taiwanartist.tw/GSR/gsr08-3.html</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">《倒牛奶的女僕》, Johannes Vermeer, Johannes Vermeer, Image from</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E7%B9%AA%E7%95%AB </span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 33px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">德國藝術（15th-16th ）The Northern Renaissance (Germany)</h1><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【藝術家】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">阿爾布雷德‧杜勒(Albrecht Duerer，1471~1528):《亞當和夏娃》《憂鬱》《啟示錄四騎士》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">格魯奈瓦德(M. Gruenewald，1470/80~1528):《基督受刑圖》《基督升天圖》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">小漢斯‧霍爾班(Hans Holbein the Younger，1497~1545):《喬治‧吉茨像》《英王亨利肖像》《邁耶的聖母子》</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【起源】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">中世紀結束時，德國也出現了與其他歐洲國家相似的狀況---城市出現、工業發展、市民階級興起。人們開始重視自然與真實，同時對科學知識產生興趣，城市出現了人文主義思維。德國並沒有可復興的古典文化，「德國文藝復興」挪用了義大利的名詞，指德國15世紀資產階級文化藝術的興起，以及新的藝術觀及世界觀。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【風格】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">德國文藝復興時期的藝術受到義大利和尼德蘭藝術的影響，同時保有德國日耳曼民族特點---具強烈宗教感，重視理性及思考，注意細節的描繪。15世紀的德國主要流行的是哥德式藝術那種激動不安的外表和強烈運動感的形象，同時彌漫著濃厚的宗教思維。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">德國藝術家在此時產生了許多驚人的成就，如杜勒、小霍爾班、格魯奈瓦德等人。他們的創作包含版畫、油畫以及線造型所表現的素描作品影響甚廣，同時將北歐藝術與義大利藝術相結合。其中杜勒兼有北歐人細膩、精緻和個性的特點，以及南歐藝術的科學性、優美、理想化。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【後續】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">德國文藝復興榮景短暫，只維持從15世紀末到16世紀初約30年的時間。當時的藝術家技巧純熟，作品中也反映了德國的社會歷史問題。16世紀德國爆發了以馬丁‧路德為首的宗教改革，又爆發了農民戰爭。宗教改革對於藝術的影響是消極的，因此16世紀下半葉以後，德國藝術發展逐漸沉默。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">【延伸閱讀】</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">書:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">何政廣(2009)。德國文藝復興最偉大畫家：丟勒。台北:藝術家。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">朱艷輝、葉桂紅(譯)(2009)。丟勒和他的時代。北京:大學出版社。(威爾赫姆‧韋措爾特)</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">李紹明(2003)。歐羅巴的黃金時代︰北部歐洲（公元1500~1675）。山東:畫報出版社。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">網路:</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">Sophy Sophie 西方藝術史 德國</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">http://sophy-western-art.blogspot.com/2013/05/3-2-2-german-renaissance-art.html</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: " padding:="" display:="" color:="" font-family:="" noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:=""/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, " noto="" sans="" microsoft="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-wrap:="">北方文藝復興的藝術</span>&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border</p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('91','17','恭喜****成交一件吳冠中 水鄉人家字畫','','吳冠中','','1','恭喜****已439萬人民幣 成交一件吳冠中 水鄉人家字畫','1741405416','1741405416','<p>恭喜****已439萬人民幣 成交一件吳冠中 水鄉人家字畫</p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('92','22','從精神到轉化到藝術材料的渡變－白色記憶藝術空間《深層的視覺維度》 黃耀鋅x陳奎延x王維Mnookin 創作三人展','','焦點新聞','','1','於白色記憶藝術空間所舉辦的展覽「深層的視覺維度」除了探討了創作者們在視覺藝術層面的多元性，更開闢了三位藝術家在個人經驗與創作之間的路徑，我們可以藉由展覽窺見生活與感性經驗的交融，以及在轉至媒材後的變化。白色記憶藝術空間《深層的視覺維度》創作三人展，展場外觀實紀。【陳奎延 CHEN Kuei-yen(b.1981)】藝術家陳奎延。首先可以談及藝術家陳奎延的創作，其深受個人經驗與內在情感的影響，他的近&hellip;','1741421332','1741421332','<p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;">於白色記憶藝術空間所舉辦的展覽</span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/WhiteMemoryArtSpace" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(228, 33, 68); transition: 0.2s ease-in-out; line-height: 1.9; margin: 10px 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">「深層的視覺維度」</span></a><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;">除了探討了創作者們在視覺藝術層面的多元性，更開闢了三位藝術家在個人經驗與創作之間的路徑，我們可以藉由展覽窺見生活與感性經驗的交融，以及在轉至媒材後的變化。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/53491741421082.jpg" width="500" height="625"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">白色記憶藝術空間《深層的視覺維度》創作三人展，展場外觀實紀。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">【陳奎延 CHEN Kuei-yen(b.1981)】</span></h3><p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/12251741421083.jpg" width="500" height="500"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">藝術家陳奎延。</span><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"></span></span><br/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">首先可以談及藝術家陳奎延的創作，其深受個人經驗與內在情感的影響，他的近期作品靈感源於一次極具震撼力的夢境。在夢中，他走進一間由七彩礦石構成的房間，這個空間既璀璨奪目又令人不安，鋒利的礦石邊緣帶有潛在的威脅，使他產生一種既迷戀又恐懼的情緒。然而，這個夢境的影響並未止步於此，之後的日子裡，這個場域逐漸成為他心中的「內在房間」（Inner Realm），成為一種冥想、整理內心狀態與療癒的方式。他更將這一夢境具象化於作品《夢室》（Room in the Dream）之中，試圖將夢境的視覺語言轉化為現實中的藝術表達。</span></span></p><p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/12441741421089.jpg" width="500" height="391"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳奎延CHEN Kuei-yen｜《夢室》(Room in the Dream)｜73x91cm(30F)｜壓克力顏料於畫布 Acrylic on canvas｜2024。</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/71721741421089.jpg" width="500" height="376"/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《深層的視覺維度》創作三人展，陳奎延水晶與礦石作品系列(右方) ，展場實紀。</span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">然而，這個夢境並非系列作品的唯一主導因素。陳奎延提及，夢境所帶來的視覺啟發與他在現實生活中經歷的焦慮症狀相互交織。現實世界的壓力使他感受到如礦石般無形的壓迫，使空間變得緊縮，呼吸變得困難，這種感受與夢境中的礦石環繞有著驚人的相似之處。他將水晶與礦石視為象徵性的視覺元素，代表著外在世界的資訊、渴望與妄想，也象徵內在的恐懼、焦慮與壓力。例如，在作品《樂、美麗與掙扎》（The Joy, Beauty and Struggle）中，一位女子彷彿被周遭的水晶照耀與滋潤，但同時也受壓迫而難以抗拒對外在世界的渴望，形成一種矛盾的情感狀態。</span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/31231741421096.jpg" width="500" height="806"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳奎延CHEN Kuei-yen｜《樂、美麗與掙扎》(The Joy, Beauty and Struggle)｜29x16.5x1.2cm(2F)｜壓克力顏料於木板 Acrylic on Panel｜2024。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://d3d9mb8xdsbq52.cloudfront.net/s3/250220/192724mzo.jpg" width="500" height="301"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳奎延CHEN Kuei-yen｜《床》(Bed)｜17x28cm(2F)｜壓克力顏料於畫布 Acrylic on canvas｜2024。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在這一系列作品中，「人」作為另一個重要的視覺元素，許多角色以赤裸的形象呈現，象徵著最原始、真實的自己。這些形象沒有任何衣物來遮蔽，使所有情緒與感受變得更加切身，直接面對外在世界的影響。陳奎延將藝術視為心理療癒的過程，他將壓力、焦慮與痛苦轉化為藝術創作，並以二元對立的方式來詮釋人與世界的關係。他將世界比喻為蛋殼，而個體則是蛋黃，蛋白則象徵人所感知的外在現象。這種對立與平衡的思考，成為他創作的重要核心。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/75581741421107.jpg" width="500" height="641"/></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳奎延CHEN Kuei-yen｜《靜默的寶石光》(The Jewel’s light in the Silence)｜30x24cm(4F)｜壓克力顏料於畫布 Acrylic on canvas｜2024。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在技法與媒材方面，陳奎延此次運用了厚塗顏料繪畫技法，並嘗試融合進不同以往的態度與價值觀。他選擇將調色錯誤或廢棄顏料應用於作品之中，例如在作品《靜默的寶石光》（The Jewel’s Light in the Silence）中，他描繪了一位聖母，而畫布側面則使用了調色盤上廢棄的顏料，象徵聖母在面對外在黑暗時仍然保有慈悲的精神。這一創作方式不僅重新定義了傳統繪畫的邏輯，也呈現了藝術家對於「接受美好與不美好並存」的獨特觀點。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/78311741421108.jpg" width="500" height="347"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《深層的視覺維度》創作三人展，陳奎延作品(左方)，展場實紀。</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">此外，他的創作思維始終圍繞著「痛苦」與「生命歷程」的關係。他認為，快樂與痛苦並非絕對分明的兩極，而是相互交錯的存在，每個人當下的情緒往往是多種情感的混合。他將人生中的經歷比喻為礦石的形成，在擠壓、碰撞與結晶的過程中，痛苦與快樂相互作用，最終成為閃耀的結晶。因此，他的創作不僅是對個人情緒的表達，更是一種對生命歷程的詮釋。陳奎延的藝術作品，從夢境的啟發，到現實焦慮的映射，透過象徵性的視覺語言與創作技法，勾勒出一個既壓迫又釋放、既沉重又閃耀的世界。</span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/96171741421114.jpg" width="500" height="299"/></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">陳奎延CHEN Kuei-yen｜《明光》(The Light)｜19.5x33cm(3F)｜壓克力顏料於畫布 Acrylic on canvas｜2024。</span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">同樣地，藝術家黃耀鋅的創作歷程近年也來經歷了一場重大的轉變，從過去長期關注社會議題與批判性探討，轉向以個人生活經驗為核心，透過繪畫直觀呈現於畫布之上，直面複雜的感性轉折。這種轉變不僅帶來了創作上的新挑戰，也使他重新審視自身與藝術的關係。長期以來，他在作品中探討外在世界的議題，或許某種程度上也是對自身問題的一種逃避。然而，經歷了超過十年的創作階段後，他開始意識到這樣的模式已經漸漸消磨了自己的創作動力。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://d3d9mb8xdsbq52.cloudfront.net/s3/250220/184911acn.jpg" width="500" height="376"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《深層的視覺維度》創作三人展，黃耀鋅2015-2018作品系列，展場實紀。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://d3d9mb8xdsbq52.cloudfront.net/s3/250218/122045uxs.jpg" width="500" height="347"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">黃耀鋅-《我願因為聚光而吐出真心-草圖》。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">直至幾年前，他申請了金車藝文中心的個展，在這個非營利空間中，他決定嘗試新的風格與媒材，將多年來累積的草圖與生活事件轉化為作品，這樣的過程對他而言，既是一種新的探索，也是一種釋放。過去，黃耀鋅的創作多是透過對外在世界的反思來展開，而這次，他選擇將自己的經歷與腦海中的想像作為主軸，讓創作更直覺、更純粹。他認為，放空與靈光一閃的靈感並非對立，而是相互影響、並存的狀態——放空的狀態讓思緒自由遊走，而來自外界刺激的靈感則能與腦中的想像交織，形成獨特的創作能量。</p><p><img src="https://d3d9mb8xdsbq52.cloudfront.net/s3/250220/184931kev.jpg" width="500" height="376"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《深層的視覺維度》創作三人展，黃耀鋅作品系列，展場實紀。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"></span></span></span></span></span><br/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://d3d9mb8xdsbq52.cloudfront.net/s3/250218/095311uth.jpg" width="500" height="625"/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">黃耀鋅 HUANG Yao-hsin｜《時間的魔法師》(The Wizard of Time)｜73x91cm(30F)｜壓克力顏料於畫布 Acrylic on canvas｜2023。</span></span></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('93','22','紐約現代藝術博物館（MoMA）攜手香港M+簽訂合作協議，兩大藝術機構將展開多項跨國合作','','藝術品','','1','歷經一年的討論，紐約現代藝術博物館（MoMA）與位於香港西九文化區的當代藝術館M+正式簽署合作協議。這項協議的內容包括使雙方在未來共享展覽、學術研究資源以及贊助機會的媒合開發…等，藉此進一步深化彼此的合作關係。全球地緣政治自川普當選後持續處於緊張局勢升溫之際，尤其中美兩方更是如此，原因歸咎於川普政府對來自香港及中國大陸的進口商品額外加徵10%的關稅，此舉進一步加重了香港製造業和出口商的負擔，引起中&hellip;','1741421470','1741421470','<p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">歷經一年的討論，紐約現代藝術博物館（MoMA）與位於香港西九文化區的當代藝術館M+正式簽署合作協議。這項協議的內容包括使雙方在未來共享展覽、學術研究資源以及贊助機會的媒合開發…等，藉此進一步深化彼此的合作關係。全球地緣政治自川普當選後持續處於緊張局勢升溫之際，尤其中美兩方更是如此，原因歸咎於川普政府對來自香港及中國大陸的進口商品額外加徵10%的關稅，此舉進一步加重了香港製造業和出口商的負擔，引起中國官方不少反彈，因此本次兩大機構的合作也備受外界關注。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/42281741421458.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">香港，2021年11月20日，位於九龍西環球貿易廣場塔前的 M+ 現代藝術博物館。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">直至近期，MoMA公開舉行了合作簽約儀式，宣布今年度這項重要的合作關係。負責其營運資金籌措的香港西九文化區管理局（以下簡稱WCKDA）官員表示，像M+這樣大規模的藝術機構勢必會面臨日益攀升的營運成本，此外，疫情後的參觀人數也尚未恢復至過往水平，為機構的發展帶來了諸多難題與挑戰，因此這一合作機會對於M+來說無疑一大助益。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">與此同時，這次合作顯示了MoMA與亞洲的大型藝術機構邁出了重要的一步，這次建立的類夥伴關係裡面，主要涵蓋六大領域的合作，其中包括策展的學術研究與藏品保存、館方人員的培訓，以及未來在展覽上的共同策劃。這項協議可以視作WCKDA為了拓展國際合作網絡的更大戰略之一，使其全球合作夥伴數量增加至20多間知名博物館。回顧去年3月，在香港舉辦的一場文化高峰會上，WKCDA宣布已與多家國際機構簽署超過十幾份合作協議，其中包含法國龐畢度中心（Centre Pompidou）、英國泰德美術館（Tate）和畢卡索博物館（Picasso Museum）。然而，M+的館員表示，這次與MoMA的協議是創館迄今為止規模最為龐大的合作案。</p><p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/56811741421458.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">M+ 館長 Suhanya Raffel 與 MoMA 館長 Glenn Lowry 簽署協議。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">M+自2021年正式對外開放，展覽與活動兼具多元，且館藏豐富，其中包含收藏家烏利．希克（Uli Sigg）捐贈的大量中國當代藝術作品。儘管有許多優良的藏品，但在營運模式的持續性上仍有很大進步空間，因此這項新的合作協議提供了能讓這座年輕的美術館進一步接觸像MoMA這樣具有較長歷史的機構，向其學習運營模式，鞏固自身在國際上的特殊性與穩定性。</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">延伸閱讀：<a href="https://artemperor.tw/focus/4438" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(228, 33, 68); transition: 0.2s ease-in-out; line-height: 1.9; margin: 10px 0px; word-break: break-word;">耗時6年竣工 香港 M+ 下週開幕 ! 6檔特展超過1500件「M+藏品」呈現立足香港的現當代藝術視野</a></span></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">M+館長華安雅（Suhanya Raffel）在這次的儀式上透過比喻來表示「我們（香港M+）不再是一座孤島」除此之外，她也強調目前藝術機構在國際間的趨勢，並提到全球各大博物館通常透過藝術品借展協議與國際機構合作，以因應有限的館藏與資源。（這類合作模式在國際關係與文化機構之間十分常見，主要用來確立研究合作或文化交流的意向，作為正式合約前的基礎。）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">另方面對於MoMA而言，此合作可鞏固其在香港，甚至說部分亞洲的影響力。儘管香港自視為與紐約、倫敦並列的金融中心，在商業活動的部分有著蓬勃的發展，但是在博物館、美術館生態的層面仍未能與這些國際文化重鎮相提並論。即將卸任的MoMA館長葛倫·洛瑞（Glenn Lowry）在聲明中表示，「透過與M+的合作，我們能夠探索新的策展方向，並且在全球擴展觀眾的參與度。」</p><p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/55971741421458.jpg" width="500" height="263"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">M+在西九文化區裡面佔據了相當大部分的參觀人流。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">自2021年擔任WKCDA執行長的馮程淑儀（Betty Fung）在接受外媒採訪時表示，機構至今仍在發展籌資模式，並希望能效仿西方同行，試圖與私人捐助者、基金會等建立更緊密的關係，接續也補充到，資金的開發只是此次協議的一部分，未來美術館仍有許多地方需要學習及參考。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">目前看來，對兩個機構來說在這次合作底下都可以看出各自的目標以及野心，也令外界更加期待這樣的攜手下，藝術生態在國際範疇下會有甚麼變動。值得注意的是，馮程淑儀在今年2月曾向當地媒體表示出警示，香港政府於2008年立法設立了一份約275億港幣（約115億台幣）基金，至今若是無外部資金挹注，極有可能面臨枯竭的風險，WKCDA於2023年度的報告裡指出，其財務赤字已超過13億港幣。若根據2022至2023年度數據來看，西九文化區的美術館總共吸引了超過400萬名訪客，其中M+就佔據了270萬人次，而鄰近由管理局管轄的另一間博物館則吸引125萬人次，可見M+對於整個區域的藝文生態有著一定的重要程度，足以帶來巨大的影響。</p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('94','22','袁廣鳴個展「向黑潛行」，從日常戰爭到扁平世界，探討全球化下的黑暗深處','','藝術品','','1','TKG+於2025年初春推出袁廣鳴最新個展「向黑潛行」，展覽以「黑」為相互連結的概念下，串連三件來自不同起點的新作。除了展出2024年「第60屆威尼斯國際美術雙年展」（La Biennale di Venezia）所呈現的兩件新作《日常戰爭》和《扁平世界》，更展出以1995年的早期作品《呼吸的黑光》為概念而延伸的新作《呼吸的黑洞》。透過三件作品來構築一條遞進的思想軌跡，從日常的潰散到感知的挑戰，再&hellip;','1741421714','1741421714','<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; word-break: break-word; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">TKG+於2025年初春推出袁廣鳴最新個展「向黑潛行」，展覽以「黑」為相互連結的概念下，串連三件來自不同起點的新作。除了展出2024年「第60屆威尼斯國際美術雙年展」（La Biennale di Venezia）所呈現的兩件新作《日常戰爭》和《扁平世界》，更展出以1995年的早期作品《呼吸的黑光》為概念而延伸的新作《呼吸的黑洞》。透過三件作品來構築一條遞進的思想軌跡，從日常的潰散到感知的挑戰，再到全球化的觀看壓縮，黑暗作為核心意象貫穿其中，以此對當代生存狀態進行了一場徹底而深刻的反思。</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">延伸閱讀 ▌</span><a href="https://artemperor.tw/focus/5974" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(228, 33, 68); transition: 0.2s ease-in-out; line-height: 1.9; margin: 10px 0px; word-break: break-word;">2024威尼斯雙年展台灣館 「袁廣鳴：日常戰爭」盛大開幕，突顯自由與人類處境之思辨</a></h3><p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/90691741421705.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span class="picinfo" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 13px; width: 800px; margin: 5px 0px 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.7;">《向黑潛行—袁廣鳴個展》展出現場。</span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">展覽從《日常戰爭》的影像敘事展開，並首次公開三件精細幕後手稿。袁廣鳴表示，相較於威尼斯雙年展台灣館的場地，此次於TKG+的呈現，在尺幅及聲響場域上較不受限，因此得以更加完整；而三件手稿更是呈現出袁廣鳴於製做期間構思作品的路徑。《日常戰爭》這件單頻道錄像中描繪了一個中產階級男性的單身套房，在這樣一個表面秩序井然的日常場景中，一股無形的力量打破寧靜，房間轉瞬間化為廢墟。片刻之後，一切重回初始狀態，彷彿災難從未發生。作品循環的敘事結構巧妙模糊了日常與災難、真實與虛構的界限，揭示出戰爭並非遠離的真實，而是日常生活中無聲的裂縫，逐步侵蝕我們的感知與存在。光線閃爍與空間崩解的交替畫面，營造出一種荒謬卻真實的緊張感，讓觀者感知到日常表層的平靜，或許只是危機的隱秘前奏。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/58541741421705.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《日常戰爭》展出現場。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/17081741421705.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《日常戰爭》幕後草圖，展出現場。</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/19491741421706.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《日常戰爭》幕後草圖－側面，2025。壓克力顏料，麥克筆，粉彩，雷射，牛皮卡紙，60 x 90 cm。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">踏入展場內部，身體將被黑暗所包覆，而牆面上一股微弱的光暈隨之擴張與收縮。《呼吸的黑洞》是袁廣鳴 1995 年在德國卡爾斯魯造形藝術學院求學時期的實驗創作《呼吸的黑光》的概念延伸，將「黑光」這一物理上不可能存在的意象具象化為一個律動場域，鋁板與夜光粉構成作品的核心，隨著機械驅動，鋁板緩慢移動，宛如黑洞的「呼吸」。黑光在此成為象徵語言，既暗示光的缺席，又蘊含能量的積聚與釋放，挑戰觀者對黑暗的固有認知。這片律動的黑暗，不僅呼應黑洞吞噬一切的物理意象，更展現黑暗作為生成與生命力場域的雙重屬性。觀者在光與黑的交界處，視覺邊界被模糊，身體感知重新啟動，得以探索存有的根基。黑暗不再僅是虛無或恐懼的象徵，而是一個充滿力量與希望的隱秘場所，為展覽提供了感知與思想層面的橋樑與深化。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/62641741421706.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《呼吸的黑洞》，1995-2024。光動力裝置(夜光粉．紫外線光．電控軌道系統），尺寸依場域而定。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/67081741421706.jpg" width="500" height="333"/></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">《呼吸的黑洞》展出現場。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">展場的最深處，播放著快速切換的風景。不同以往使用自己所攝製的影像內容，《扁平世界》以 Google 街景資料庫為基礎，透過固定的線性透視與穩定運動，挑選100個國家305街景串聯為無止境的數位旅程。影片的循環結構隱喻全球化秩序的幻象，連續的街景成為現代技術體系的象徵，揭示人類漂浮與失根的矛盾處境與現代觀看方式的壓縮與疏離，同時也消解了地理的深度與身體的在場感。地圖從地方記憶與傳說的載體，變為技術與權力的象徵；觀看則退化為點對點的跳躍，空間的厚度與情感隨之消失。袁廣鳴將這種「扁平世界」推至極致，讓觀者在冷靜而壓迫的影像中直面技術操控的矛盾與迷霧。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('95','22','「把生活與藝術打成一片」用筆觸譜寫內心世界：藝術家黃志超辭世，享壽84歲','','藝術品','','1','藝術家黃志超辭世，享壽84歲。黃志超1941年生於廈門鼓浪嶼，祖籍湖南長沙，好吃零食，愛喝可樂，因此有著「可樂居士」、「樂可馬」等別號。幼時在上海、臺北、海門等地流轉，使他習得閩南語、上海話、北京話，並耳聞日語、福州話、廣東話。他曾回憶道，童年時在嘉義上學期間，老師混雜國語、臺語和日語教學，令他學得一口充滿臺灣特色的國語；那時，耳邊常聽到「阿山阿山賣豆干」的叫賣聲，眼前則浮現出火車呼嘯而過、綠油油&hellip;','1741421869','1741421869','<p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">藝術家黃志超辭世，享壽84歲。黃志超1941年生於廈門鼓浪嶼，祖籍湖南長沙，好吃零食，愛喝可樂，因此有著「可樂居士」、「樂可馬」等別號。幼時在上海、臺北、海門等地流轉，使他習得閩南語、上海話、北京話，並耳聞日語、福州話、廣東話。他曾回憶道，童年時在嘉義上學期間，老師混雜國語、臺語和日語教學，令他學得一口充滿臺灣特色的國語；那時，耳邊常聽到「阿山阿山賣豆干」的叫賣聲，眼前則浮現出火車呼嘯而過、綠油油甘蔗田的動人景象。這些鄉土記憶和市集風情，從小就在他的心中悄然種下對生活細節與文化符號的敏感，為後來藝術創作中對色彩、線條和空間的獨特處理奠定了基礎。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">自14歲起，黃志超開始學習西洋素描、油畫及中國書畫，他曾騎著腳踏車，攜畫架奔赴蘆洲、士林、淡水等地寫生，以訓練眼手協調。18歲時便立志成為職業畫家，先後拜訪多位大師，其中對他影響深遠的包括席德進與吳學讓，經由席德進的推薦，黃志超向吳學讓學了將近六年的國畫與篆刻。長期請教這兩位前輩，黃志超對臺灣民間藝術與古代服飾、民歌、木偶戲等鄉土文化的魅力而吸引，進而轉化為創作靈感，這段經歷也成為他繪畫脈絡中的重要滋養。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/28371741421866.jpg" width="500" height="397"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">藝術家黃志超。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在多年的國畫與篆刻訓練後，黃志超更於1965年開始跟隨李仲生學習現代畫。李仲生主張以精神傳遞精神的現代教學法，要求他拋棄舊有技法，追求藝術本質中那獨有的自我表達。</span></span></span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">重建的過程中，最終找到了屬於自己的創作路徑——那種「畫出一張不像畫的畫」的創作理念，強調藝術應該摒棄既有理論和技法的束縛，純粹以自我本能和內心的感受進行表達。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">此外，他也在一次偶然的機會中發現，古代蠟染中自然或人為形成的斑駁與龜裂，既帶有濃厚的鄉土氣息，又具有現代感與透明感，這啟示他運用蠟染技法表現現代繪畫。即便面臨保守派的非議，他仍執著於研究，最終能夠運用自如，甚至寫下關於蠟染的專著，為自己的創作語言增添了全新的視覺層次。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">1971年，他應邀出國訪問展出，自香港、日本、夏威夷一路展至洛杉磯、舊金山，再到華盛頓，最終定居紐約這座世界藝術之都。正是在這充滿挑戰與機遇的環境中，黃志超的藝術觀念得以徹底重塑，從「書法中的行筆走勢」到「北宋潑墨與唐代狂草」的自由揮灑，他以極富速度感的筆觸，展現出藝術的自我本能。面對現代科技與都市快節奏的生活，他一方面以修補古董維生，一方面不斷從中國古文物和傳統民俗中尋找靈感，試圖將東方的美學與西方的現代性巧妙融合。</span></p><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/17421741421866.jpg" width="500" height="385"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">黃志超《富春山居》183.5x142cm，2014，複合媒材、畫布。</span><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在紐約這個全球文化交匯的都市中，黃志超逐漸體會到：只有將東方傳統文化與現代藝術的自由精神有機結合，才能真正創造出屬於現代東方的獨特語言。從那時起，他開始更有意識地回歸東方文化，力求創作出能與西方藝術平起平坐、並具有民族自信的作品。</span></span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">黃志超一生對藝術的探索從未停止，他不僅在技法上勇於創新，還在理念上不斷推翻舊我，追尋更真實的自我表達。在四十歲到五十歲（1981–1991）的時期，他不滿足於單一的表現形式，開始刻意用力刮、線刻或留白，嘗試創作出「不像畫」的作品。他認為，藝術家應該把生活與生命完全結合，不僅僅是技法上的熟練，而更要反映出內心深處的情感與思想。在畫友的鼓勵下，他堅定地提出「中國人要畫中國人的現代畫」的理念，主張從中國傳統文人畫中吸取靈感，融合現代美學，創造出獨特而不落俗套的藝術風格。</span></p></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><img src="https://wniw.khunia.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/13951741421867.jpg" width="500" height="413"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">黃志超《Spring Journey春遊》140x170cm，2020，複合媒材、畫布。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">進入五十歲到六十歲（1991–2001）的階段，黃志超重新拾起毛筆和宣紙，利用潑墨與狂草飛白的筆觸，展現出一種不經修飾、直接流露內心情緒的藝術風格。那種行筆如同高速公路上疾駛的汽車般的迅速與自如，正是他多年來對書法與中國筆墨運用的最終體現。透過這種隨心所欲的創作方式，他在畫布上再現了心靈深處那股強烈的、幾近本能的爆發力，創作出「色極觀系列」、「新樂園系列」和「情色系列」等極具個人風格的作品。</span></span></span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p><br style="box-sizing: border-box; content: &quot;&quot;; padding: 5px; display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, PMingLiU, Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-wrap: wrap;">在黃志超的創作自述中，他談到：「藝術是在反映生活，提昇美感，創造新的視覺經驗……在紐約這樣的環境裡，才真正可以做到完全隨心所欲地爆發出自我個性的本能。」正是這份對藝術真諦的追求，驅使他創作出「色極觀系列」、「新樂園系列」及「情色系列」等具突破性意涵的作品。他的筆觸時而狂草飛白、時而隨性自發，猶如在高速公路上馳騁的駕駛，將中西藝術精神巧妙融合，展現出一位現代藝術家對於自我再肯定的獨到見解。</span></p></p>','1');
INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('96','22','徐文君：2025佳士得香港春拍雙城聯動，藝術購藏的黃金時機？','','藝術品','','1','導言：每年開春的香港拍賣季，都是觀察市場走向重要的風向標。本季拍賣，佳士得香港一改往年的拍賣日程，不僅提前至3月，與巴塞爾藝術展同期舉辦，還採取了香港與上海雙城聯動的策略。在拍賣之前，佳士得二十及二十一世紀晚間拍賣主管徐文君對雅昌拍賣圖錄分享了此次拍賣的籌備思路和市場預期。本季拍賣，除了有高價作品如巴斯奇亞和瑪格麗特的作品上拍，估價超過5000萬港幣。此外，這次更多的作品定價在2000萬港幣上下，&hellip;','1742556727','1742556727','<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 176, 80);">導言：</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">每年開春的香港拍賣季，都是觀察市場走向重要的風向標。本季拍賣，佳士得香港一改往年的拍賣日程，不僅提前至3月，與巴塞爾藝術展同期舉辦，還採取了香港與上海雙城聯動的策略。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">在拍賣之前，</span><strong>佳士得二十及二十一世紀晚間拍賣主管徐文君</strong><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">對</span><strong>雅昌拍賣圖錄</strong><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">分享了此次拍賣的籌備思路和市場預期。本季拍賣，除了有高價作品如</span><strong>巴斯奇亞</strong><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">和</span><strong>瑪格麗特</strong><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">的作品上拍，估價超過5000萬港幣。此外，這次更多的作品定價在2000萬港幣上下，</span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">徐文君指出，當前藝術市場的狀態取決於作品本身和定價策略，而非單純的市場好壞。佳士得此次拍賣希望透過極具性價比的作品</span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">吸引更多藏家參與。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2025年，藏家在市場中的心態趨於謹慎，更加重視藝術家的長期價值和作品的展覽記錄。有鑑於此，佳士得此次在選購品和定價上充分考慮了不同地區的藏家偏好，力求在全球化與本土化之間找到平衡。</span></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">今年佳士得香港「二十及二十一世紀」春拍選與香港巴塞爾同期舉辦，這是出於怎樣的考量？</span></strong><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px;">徐文君：</strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: inherit;">&nbsp;3月巴塞爾期間，全球藏家都會聚集香港。歐美藏家甚至會特地飛過來，因為有值得一看的作品、展覽、藝博會、拍賣會等。選擇這個時間點舉辦拍賣，也是為了藉助巴塞爾的全球影響力，吸引更多藏家的關注，尤其是一級市場的藏家。</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px;">3月與巴塞爾同期舉辦拍賣，是為了與整個藝術圈團結一致，共同推動市場。這個時間點不僅有我們的拍賣，還有M+美術館的畢卡索展覽、巴塞爾藝博會以及香港畫廊的展覽，整體氛圍非常團結。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">此次佳士得香港春拍拉開了2025年拍賣的帷幕，對於當前的藝術市場，你們有怎樣的預期和判斷？</span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">徐文君：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">市場的好壞取決於作品和價格，而非統一的市場狀態。我們的責任是選擇對的藝術家和作品，並定出適當的價格。例如，我們在今年倫敦拍賣中成功拍出了弗朗西斯·培根和瑪格麗特的作品，特別是瑪格麗特的作品《無限感激》以1031.5萬英鎊成交，這證明了我們團隊在徵集方面的努力。我們觀察到市場對超現實主義藝術的需求增加，因此我們也在推動這一板塊。</span></span></span></strong><br/></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><br/></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">基於目前的市場，本季春拍在徵集時，選件的標準及定價策略是怎樣的？</span></strong></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">徐文君：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">此次拍賣的作品定價多在2000萬港幣左右，是一個非常吸引藏家的價格區間。我們也有一些高價作品，如巴斯奇亞和瑪格麗特的作品，估價超過5000萬港幣。這些高價作品的針對性較強，不是每個藏家都會參與。因此在整體作品的價位上，我們估價還是保持保守，以確保更多藏家能夠參與。同時，我們也希望透過部分高價作品吸引頂級藏家的注意。</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><br/></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">在徵件過程中，藏家對於2025年市場的心態是怎樣的？</span></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">徐文君：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">藏家對藝術品的收藏趨於謹慎，他們會仔細挑選藝術家和作品。這種謹慎態度是好事，說明藏家更注重藝術家的長期價值和作品的展覽記錄。他們會研究藝術家的展覽歷史、出版記錄以及國際影響力，而不是因為一時的市場熱度而做出購買決定。我們的責任是在對的時候選擇對的作品，並以適當的價格推薦給對的藏家。例如，我們在去年秋拍中推出了莫內和梵谷的作品，吸引了亞洲不同地區的顧客競投。我們在不同市場狀態下會做出相對應的調整。</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><strong style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><br/>