19 in.（48.2 釐米）直徑， 布盒','21000000.00','<p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">這款非凡的充電器是大型乾隆龍盤的罕見例子，裝飾有釉上鐵紅色琺瑯描繪的巧妙彩繪龍，結合豐富的釉下鈷藍色波浪和雲朵。盤子直徑 48.2 釐米，底部刻有字跡斑斕的釉下青乾隆篆印。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>這道帥氣的菜極有可能是在乾隆初期製作的。該器皿在尺寸和裝飾上都與北京故宮博物院收藏的雍正時期的釉下青鐵紅琺瑯裝飾盤極為相似（見<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《故宮博物院珍品全集》第</em>36卷，<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">釉下紅青花瓷（III），</em>香港，2000年，第245頁。 第 223 期）。雍正盤的底部有一個雙圓圈內的六字釉下釉下藍色標記。梅澤紀念館的另一件雍正作品已被日本當局指定為“重要藝術品”，在《<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">真由山：七十年》</em>第 1 卷，東京，1976 年，第 352 頁，第 1055 號中進行了說明。雍正和乾隆器之間的相似性表明，它們是在相對較短的時間內在清朝禦窯製造的。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>乾隆紀年早期的另一個指標是由<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">清宮</em>內府棗板初檔案中的一個條目提供的。該條目的日期為乾隆三年（相當於1738年）六月二十五日。除了獻給皇帝的其他物品外，該條目還提到：<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">義劍玄窯洪龍青雲海水大盤</em>（一種帶有紅龍、藍雲和波浪的大型玄燒菜餚）。這個條目很可能表明與當前船隻相似的菜餚。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>檔案條目中的“宣器”描述無疑是指備受推崇的明代宣德年間（1425-35 年）的瓷器。然而，1738 年呈獻給乾隆皇帝的這道菜實際上不太可能是 15</span><span _msttexthash="21372" _msthash="68" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 10.5px; position: relative; top: -0.5em; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">th</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">世紀菜，更有可能的是同時代的 （18</span><span tabindex="0" _msttexthash="21372" _msthash="70" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 10.5px; position: relative; top: -0.5em; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">th</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">世紀）的 Xuande 風格的菜餚。和他的父親（雍正皇帝 1723-35 年）和祖父（康熙皇帝 1662-1722 年）一樣，乾隆皇帝也是一位熱情且知識淵博的古董收藏家。許多為他的宮廷製作的藝術品都是以古色古香的風格製作的，事實上，有些還專門刻有“仿古”<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">的方谷</em>。與幾個世紀以來的其他鑒賞家一樣，乾隆皇帝特別欣賞宣德和成華（1464-87 年）在位的瓷器。事實上，通過研究他為某些瓷器所塗的較長銘文，可以看出，當他想讚美陶瓷器皿時，他經常將其與宣德或成化時期的作品進行比較。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>雖然在宣德時代似乎沒有完全相同的大小和設計的大型青紅龍盤倖存下來，但清代充電器上的一些裝飾元素似乎是從宣德瓷器中汲取靈感的。其中最明顯的是釉下鐵紅和釉下藍色的使用——尤其是與波浪和雲朵描繪的龍有關。早在永樂（1402-24年）年間，少量御窯製作的瓷器都以紅龍為背景。一個很好的例子是 1999 年在禦窯中發現的永樂莖碗，插圖見<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《明清禦窯瓷器——故宮博物院和景德鎮陶瓷考古新成果</em>》，北京，2016 年，第 178-9 頁，第 75 期。在這個永樂莖碗上，龍和雲被釉下銅紅色描繪，與鈷藍色的背景相映成趣。雖然釉上鐵紅在洪武（1468-98 年）和永樂年間被用於帝王瓷器，但釉下鐵紅與釉下鈷藍的組合似乎直到宣德年間才開始流行。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>一小群宣德碗，最初是有蓋的，因此有時被稱為&nbsp;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">hewan，</em>即「箱碗」，兩側裝飾有釉下藍色雲朵中的釉上鐵紅龍，上方是一條藍色湍流波。在景德鎮發現的一個這樣的碗發表在<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《明清禦窯瓷器——故宮博物院和景德鎮陶瓷考古新成果</em>》中，<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">見上</em>引，第 118 頁，第 42 期。臺北國立故宮博物院收藏了一枚這種帶蓋的碗，並收錄在臺北，1998 年，第 164-5 頁，第 55 期的<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《明代宣德瓷器精選特別展</em>》中，而另一件來自北京故宮博物院的碗，則收錄在<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《故宮博物院珍品全集》中。&nbsp;</em>第 34 卷，<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">釉下紅青花瓷 （I），</em>香港，2000 年，第 254 頁，第 230 號，第四個由珀西瓦爾·大衛爵士收藏（註冊號。PDF A778）。雖然這種佈置與當前乾隆盤側面的佈局一致，但其他宣德器皿與乾隆盤中央的裝飾相聯繫。在少數倖存的宣德瓷器上可以看到釉上鐵紅色繪製的生物與豐富的釉下鈷藍色波浪的描繪，例如北京故宮博物院的莖杯，這在&nbsp;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">The Complet 中得到了插圖e 故宮博物院珍品，</em>第 34 卷，<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">釉下紅青花瓷 （I），同上，</em>第 255 頁，第 231 號。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>與宣德時代的瓷器的聯繫也可以從當前盤子中央的龍姿中看出。盤子內側和外側的龍在雲層中漫步，從側面可以看到，而中央獎章中的龍則面向前方，四條腿都向兩側伸展，從海浪中用力躍出。這種立場的起源可以在 15 年初看到</span><span _msttexthash="21372" _msthash="72" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 10.5px; position: relative; top: -0.5em; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">th</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(58, 46, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(246, 245, 250);">世紀器皿，例如 Percival David 收藏中的莖碗（參見 Rosemary&nbsp;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">Scott，Imperial Taste： Chinese Ceramics from the Percival David Foundation，</em>三藩市，1989 年，第 63 頁，第 33 期）。在這個莖碗的側面，一條銅紅色的龍從藍色的波浪中大力躍出，面朝前方，四條腿都向兩側伸展。宣德和乾隆站姿之間的主要區別在於，雖然兩條龍基本上都面朝前，脖子在頭頂上形成一個環，而宣德龍的頭是三四張視圖，而乾隆龍的頭是全臉的。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>有趣的是，裝飾當前充電器內外牆的四條龍中的每一條都是不同的。其中 2 只是五爪生物，2 只是三爪生物——這表明 2 只與皇帝有關，2 隻與王子有關。每條龍都有不同的姿態。其中一條五爪龍被描繪成回頭看向肩膀，其姿勢類似於北京故宮博物院收藏的宣德青花龍盤牆壁上的一條龍（見<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《故宮博物全》第&nbsp;</em>34 卷，<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">釉下紅青花瓷（I）， 同上，</em>第 140 頁，第 132 期）。其中一條三爪王龍長著蝙蝠般的翅膀。帶翅膀的龍出現在永樂和宣德時期的少數青花瓷器上。其中一些有鰭，一些有腿，並且都有滾動的尾巴。這道乾隆菜上的例子沒有鰭，而是三個爪子和一個滾動的尾巴。也許更有趣的是這條帶翅膀的龍的頭部位置。它似乎在向上看，在此過程中露出了它的喉嚨和下巴的下側。這種特殊的姿勢似乎進入了雍正統治時期的皇家陶瓷曲目，作為被稱為“皇帝指示太子”的主題的一部分。1999 年 11 月 2 日，香港佳士得拍賣行售出一張張鍶箏珍藏的雍正青花瓶，編號 513。在這個花瓶的側面，兩條龍在狂風暴雨的海浪中展示——一條是強大的五爪龍，代表皇帝;另一條較小的三爪龍，代表太子，抬頭看著它的父親，露出它的喉嚨，就像現在的乾隆盤和北京故宮博物院裡類似的雍正盤一樣。雖然這種菜類型的雍正和乾隆版本極為相似，但可以注意到，在雍正盤上，兩側的兩條三爪龍相互跟隨，五爪生物也是如此，而在乾隆版本中，三爪龍和五爪龍交替出現。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>一個與現在的器皿幾乎相同的大型乾隆盤子被南京博物院收藏，並包含在 1995 年在香港舉行的展覽“<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">康熙雍正乾隆”</em>展覽中，展品 81（和封面插圖）。本次展覽中來自南京博物院的作品最初是奉天宮（現遼寧省瀋陽故宮博物院）和熱河宮（現河北省澄河頤和園）的清朝皇室的一部分。另一道以乾隆為標誌的此類菜餚在 Seikado Bunk 中o 美術館，在&nbsp;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">Seikado zo Shincho toji 中插圖。Keitokuchin kanyo no bi，</em>&nbsp;（清朝瓷器收集在 Seikado.景德鎮禦窯之美），東京，2006 年，第 53 期，以及出光收藏中的另一件作品，收錄在出<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">光收藏的中國陶瓷</em>中，東京，1987 年，第 956 期。周麗麗（編輯）在上海博物館藏品研究綱要中包括了另一種類型的乾隆龍菜&nbsp;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">– 清代雍正玄統御窯瓷</em>器，上海，2014 年，第 3-5 頁。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>假設現在的這道菜確實可以追溯到乾隆時代初期，這意味著它是在所有帝窯院長中最著名和最受尊敬的唐英任期內製作的，唐英從 1728 年到 1736 年擔任常駐助理，當時他接替年夕堯擔任主任——他從 1736 年到 1756 年擔任該職位。由於他是一位非常有成就的陶器家，在陶瓷設計方面具有特別的技巧，因此唐英帝窯製作的瓷器因其高品質和非凡的裝飾而特別珍貴。唐英特別擅長的領域之一是古代器皿的生產——無論要複製的古代物品的方面是它的釉料、形狀、裝飾技術還是裝飾圖案。張法英編<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">著的《</em>清代陶蓉文獻》，北京，2012 年，第 148-52 頁指出，較小的物品從皇宮送到景德鎮的唐英那裡以便複製，但是，對於較大的物品，例如現在的菜餚，<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>紅龍碧雲合浪，顯然對乾隆皇帝有著特殊的吸引力。考慮到與紅色相關的吉祥含義，這並不奇怪。皇帝對裝飾有五爪龍的帝王瓷器上的這種顏色組合的偏愛，不僅體現在的釉上鐵紅琺瑯龍等壯觀的菜餚上，而且在北京故宮博物院保存的清宮廷收藏的乾隆月瓶等器皿上，有一條釉下銅紅色五爪龍，有藍雲和波浪（見<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">《故宮博物院珍品全集》，&nbsp;</em>卷 36，<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">釉下紅青花瓷 （III），同上，第</em>&nbsp;233 頁，第 213 號），以及來自同一收藏的乾隆月瓶，該瓶有釉下釉紅色琺瑯五爪龍，釉下青雲和波浪（見<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">同上</em>，第 254 頁，第 232 號）。</span></p>','','九龙','','Goods/20250302/67c3d9b9d2453.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3d9c2e3875.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3d9ca5b859.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3d9d169f9d.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3d9d92b21c.jpg','','1740888540','','5','');
銘文：父乙鼎
8 in. (20.3 cm.) high','16000000.00','<p><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠牙</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">器皿象徵著王權，對商朝統治精英具有重大意義。現存最大的商代青銅器器是四目武方</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">頂</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">，高 133 釐米，重 875 公斤，於 1939 年在安陽市五關村發現，現藏於中國國家博物館。見</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">《中國</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">青銅器全集：商》第2卷，北京，1997年，第48頁，第47期。雖然巨大的</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠牙</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">器皿是專門為國王和王后製造的，但普通尺寸的</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">牙是為高級貴族保留的。現在的</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">牙有力的比例和精細的鑄造展示了晚商都安陽青銅設計和鑄造的複雜程度。</span><br _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);"/><br _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);"/><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">當前</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠牙</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">的一面內牆上的銘文寫著</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">福毅</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">（義父），後面是一張描繪</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">丁</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">食器皿的圖表。在梅音堂收藏的</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">丁</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">鼎器上可以找到相同的銘文，由 C. Deydier 插圖，梅</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">音堂收藏的中國青銅器</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">，第 1 卷附件，香港，2013 年，第 116-17 頁，第 69 號，以及上海博物館的一對</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">覺</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">，插圖為</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">《</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">陰周青銅器銘文彙編》）， 北京，1984年，第8421和8422號。</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">安養</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">博物館收藏了一枚刻</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">有鼎</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">圖的駿子，插圖</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);"></em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">見</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">《中原文武</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">》第 3 卷，河南，1986 年，第 119 頁。</span><br _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);"/><br _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);"/><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">牙鑄像具有相似的裝飾，但尺寸更大（24.4 釐米高），腿更高、更細長，在國立故宮博物院藏品《</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">香禮青銅</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">器》中有所說明，國立故宮博物院，臺北，1998 年，第 560-3 頁，第 96 號。R.W. Bagley 在&nbsp;</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">Arthur M. Sackler 收藏的 Shang Ritual Bronzes</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">&nbsp;中插圖了類似尺寸（20.8 釐米高）和裝飾的</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">牙，劍橋，馬薩諸塞州劍橋，1987 年，第 472-5 頁，第 88 號，後來在紐約佳士得拍賣，2010 年 3 月 25 日至 26 日，拍品編號 1003。其他類似的</span><em _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">獠牙</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">包括 2012 年 3 月 22 日在佳士得紐約拍賣會上售出的 22.2 釐米高，拍品編號 1508，以及紐約佳士得拍賣的邵</span><em aria-hidden="true" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">方頂</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">（20.7 釐米高），其主帶上鸠尾鸠形成</span><em aria-hidden="true" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">逵</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">龍，口</span><em aria-hidden="true" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);"></em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">緣以下窄帶中有一對</span><em aria-hidden="true" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(46, 86, 66); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">逍</em><span style="color: rgb(46, 86, 66); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 247);">龍。 權力與聲望：歐洲傑出收藏中重要的中國早期禮器青銅器，2019 年 3 月 22 日，編號 1506</span></p>','','九龙','','Goods/20250302/67c3de3677a9c.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3df5a2a358.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3df63967c0.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3df6c95215.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3df75a89b9.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3df7dc6bb0.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3df86e7fba.jpg','','1740889994','','5','');
15 ¾ in. (40 cm.) diam.','3500000.00','<p><span style="color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);">明成祖朱棣（圖一）治下之永樂（1403–1425年）盛世，立御器廠專司研製宮廷貴器，其時文物昌，工藝精，尤以青花瓷最負盛名，世稱絕品，此盤即屬其一。這類青花盤圓腹，折沿，葵口，尺寸不一，紋飾紛陳。有關永樂瓷器工藝發展與美學源流之深入探討，可參考霍吉淑（J. Harrison-Hall）著《Catalogue of Late Yuan and Ming Ceramics in the British Museum》，倫敦，第三章，頁93-97。永樂瓷器不僅為帝廷珍視，更譽滿海外，出口頻仍，尤受印度與中東地區青睞。伊斯坦堡、德黑蘭等地諸藏皆存範例，足證聲名遠播，外銷鼎盛。且當地陶器爭相依此仿製，益顯其對域外文化之深遠影響。當地傳世一件永樂青花盤，紋飾與本盤相類，以波斯文書莫臥兒帝國第五代皇帝沙賈漢款，見P. Hardie著《China’s Trade with India》，《Transactions of the Oriental Ceramic Society》，1983–1984年，頁19，圖版3、4，足見永樂青花瓷之盛譽，為歐亞諸國所崇，流傳廣遠。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><span style="color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);">此盤之纏枝菊紋固然精妙，然其一大注目之處，在於巧用極為罕見的折沿邊飾。傳世所見的同類青花盤，折沿多繞以海水波濤紋，本盤則拼以靈芝蔓草紋，別開生面。靈芝自古為中醫所重，具駐顏不老、延年益壽之效，且寓意深遠，是中國藝術的重要圖案。靈芝寓意吉祥，譬如象徵稱心如意的如意杖，即取形靈芝。盤心菊紋雍雅華貴，意涵豐富，別號延齡客，比喻長壽安康。盤壁繪飾牡丹，又稱富貴花，標誌富貴榮華，為皇家園林所栽。靈芝長春，牡丹富榮，菊花益壽，花團錦簇，纏枝妙曼，環環相織，意涵悠遠。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><span style="color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);">伊斯坦堡托卡比宮藏有一例，與本盤紋飾雷同，尺寸略小，見J. Ayers、康蕊君（R. Krahl）著《Chinese Ceramics in the Topkapi Saray Museum, Istanbul》，倫敦，1986年，卷二，頁512，編號600。紐約大都會藝術博物館亦藏一例，尺寸略小（37.8公分），見S. Valenstein著《A Handbook of Chinese Ceramics》，紐約，1989年，頁150，編號145（圖二）。伊朗阿爾達比勒殿舊藏、伊朗國家博物館古伊朗館現藏一例，尺寸略大（43.2公分），見T. Misugi著《Chinese Porcelain Collections in the Near East: Topkapi and Ardebil》，香港，1981年，頁119，編號A.35。另有一例與本盤尺寸相同，紋飾相近，折沿飾一圈纏枝蔓草紋，2009年3月19日經紐約佳士得拍賣，拍品編號712（圖三）。另一例折沿飾一圈海水波濤紋，屬上述之較常見類型，2007年5月29日經香港佳士得拍賣，拍品編號1451。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><span style="color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);">此盤來源亦相當顯赫，由著名收藏暨慈善家布華朗（Walter Francis Brown，1930–2014年）所蓄。布華朗出身美國德州，先後創立Delray Oil Inc.及 W. F. Brown Exploration Ltd兩大企業，在德州及加拿大西部的石油與天然氣勘探產業界舉足輕重。布氏對中國藝術的熱愛，萌芽於1970年代初，於紐約佳士得拍賣會裡結下不解之緣。此後他對亞洲藝術傾注畢生熱情，終身學習，鑒藏不倦，且精研宋、明、清代陶瓷，崇宋人深致，尚明清綺華。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);"/><span style="color: rgb(46, 76, 86); font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 250);">布華朗花半生逾四十載，經寰球各大拍賣會、古董商搜奇選妙，庋藏大批中國及日本藝術珍品。他與妻子Lenora樂善好施，促成德州聖安東尼奧美術館建立亞洲藝術館藏，予公衆百科全書式的亞洲藝術賞覽機會。布氏與一衆鑒藏巨擘、古董商及藝術策展人結下深厚友誼，對業界貢獻良多。他於2014年辭世，但其芳名已永載美國傳統亞洲藝術收藏史冊。</span></p>','','九龙','','Goods/20250302/67c3e1484c901.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3e1514c92a.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3e15f38734.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3e1686622a.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3e177462d9.jpg|Goods/20250302/67c3e17f20d33.jpg','','1740890501','','5','');


